hadiths[193]{hadithnumber,text}:
7371,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bhejaa.
7372,"maine Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja to unse farmaya ke tum ahle-kitab mein se aik qaum ke paas ja rahe ho. isliye sabse pahley unhein uski dawat dena ke wo Allah ko aik maanein (aur meri risalat ko maanein ( jab wo usey samajh lein to phir unhein batana ke Allah ne aik din aur raat mein un par panch namazein farz ki hain. jab wo Namaz padhney lagein to unhein batana ke Allah ne un par unke maalon mein zakat farz ki hai, jo unke ameeron se li jaeygi aur unke ghareebon ko lota di jaeygi. jab wo iska bhi iqrar kar lein to unse zakat lena aur logon ke umda maal leney se parhez karna."
7373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Muaz ! kya tumhen malum hai ke Allah ka uske bandon par kya haq hai? ''unhon-ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jantey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hai ke wo sirf usi ki ibadat karein aur uska koi Sharik na thehraein . kya tumhen malum hai phir bandon ka Allah par kya haq hai? arz kya ke Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jantey hain, farmaya ye hai ke wo unhein azab na de."
7374,"aik shakhs ne aik doosrey shakhs Qatada bin Nauman ko baar-baar Sura ikhlas padhtey suna. subah hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar is tarah waqia bayan kya jaisey wo usey kam samajhtey hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! ye sura tehai Quran ke barabar hai. Ismail bin Jafar ne Imam Malik se ye badhaya ke unse Abdur-Rehman ne, unse unke walid ne aur unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey mere bhai Qatada bin Nauman ne khabar di Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
7375,wo Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki parwarish mein thin. unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib ko aik muhim par rawaana kya. wo sahib apne sathiyon ko Namaz padhatey they aur Namaz mein khatm Sura ikhlas par kartey they. jab log wapas aaey to iska zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unse poochho ke wo ye tarze-amal kyon ikhtiyar kiye huey they. chunanche logon ne puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke wo aisa isliye kartey they ke ye Allah ki sifat hai aur main usey padhna azeez rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bata do ke Allah bhi unhein azeez rakhta hai.
7376,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo logon par raham nahi khata Allah bhi is par raham nahi khaataa.''
7377,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas they ke aap ki aik sahibzadi Zenab ke bhejey huey aik shakhs aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey ke unke ladkey jaan nikalney ki haalat mein mubtala hain aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bula rahi hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke tum ja kar unhein bata do ke Allah hi ka sab maal hai jo chahey le-ley aur jo chahey dedey aur uski bargah mein har cheez ke liye aik waqt muqarrar hai to unse kaho ke sabr karein aur is par sabr sawab ki niyat se karein. sahibzadi ne dobara aapko qism de kar kelha bheja ke aap zaroor tashrif laey. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur aap ke sath Sad-bin-Muaz aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khadey huey ( phir jab aap sahibzadi ke ghar pahunchey to ( bachcha aapko diya gaya aur uski saans ukhad rahi thi jaisey puraanii mashk ka haal hota hai. ye dekh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon mein aansu bhar aaey. is par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ye kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye rehmat hai jo Allah Taala ne apne bandon ke dilon mein rakhi hai aur Allah bhi apne unhein bandon par raham karta hai jo raham dil hotey hain.
7378,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''takleef deh baat sun kar Allah se zyada sabr karne wala koi nahi hai, kambakht mushrik kehtey hain ke Allah aulad rakhta hai aur phir bhi wo unhein maaf karta hai aur unhein rozii deta hai.''"
7379,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ghaib ki panch kunjiyaan hain, jinhein Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta ke maa k pet mein kya hai, Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta ke kal kya hoga, Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta ke barish Kab aaeygii , Allah ke siwa aur koi nahi janta ke kis jagah koi marega aur Allah ke siwa koi nahi janta ke qiyamat Kab qaaim hogi. ''"
7380,"agar tum se koi ye kehta hai ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab ko dekha to wo ghalat kehta hai kyonke Allah Taala apne barey mein khud kehta hai ke nazrein usko dekh nahi saktin aur jo koi kehta hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghaib jantey they, to ghalat kehta hai kyonke Allah Taala khud kehta hai ke ghaib ka ilm Allah ke siwa aur kisi ko nahi."
7381,"ham (shuru Islam mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey Namaz padhtey they aur kehtey they السلام على الله to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke Allah to khud hi ( السلام‏ . Mina ( hai, albatta is tarah kaha karo التحيات لله والصلوات والطيبات ، Mina padhi. Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina padhi. السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين ، Mina padhi. أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله"
7382,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah qiyamat ke din zameen ko apni muththii mein ley lega aur aasman ko apne daaein hath mein lapet lega phir farmaeyga mein badshah hun, kahan hain zameen ke baadshaah.'' Shuaib aur Zubaidi bin musaafir aur Ishaq bin Yahya ne Zohri se bayan kya aur unse abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne."
7383,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kaha kartey they ''terii izzat ki panah mangta hun ke koi maabood terey siwa nahi, teri aisi zaat hai jisey maut nahi aur jin w ins fana ho jaaengey.''"
7384,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' logon ko dozakh mein daala jaeyga (doosri sanad) aur mujh se khaleefa bin khayyaat ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yazeed bin zurea' ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Saeed-bin-abi-Aruba ne, unse Qatada ne, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne. ( teesri sanad) aur khaleefa bin khayyaat ne is hadis ko moa'tamir-bin-Sulaimaan se riwayat kya, kaha maine apne walid se suna, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''dozkhiyon ko barabar dozakh mein daala jata rahega aur wo kahey jaeygi ke kya abhi aur hai. yahan tak ke rabbul-aalameen is par apna qadam rakh dega aur phir uska ek hissey doosrey se simat jaeyga aur us waqt wo kahegii ke bas bas, teri izzat aur karam ki qasam! aur jannat mein jagah baqi reh jaeygi. yahan tak ke Allah uske liye aik aur makhlooq paida kar dega aur wo log jannat ke baqi hissey mein raheingey.''"
7385,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat mein ye dua kartey they اللهم لك الحمد أنت رب السموات والأرض ، Mina padhi. لك الحمد أنت قيم السموات والأرض ومن فيهن ، Mina padhi. لك الحمد أنت نور السموات والأرض ، Mina padhi. قولك الحق ، Mina padhi. ووعدك الحق ، Mina padhi. ولقاؤك حق ، Mina padhi. والجنة حق ، Mina padhi. والنار حق ، Mina padhi. والساعة حق ، Mina padhi. اللهم لك أسلمت ، Mina padhi. وبك آمنت ، Mina padhi. وعليك توكلت ، Mina padhi. وإليك أنبت ، Mina padhi. وبك خاصمت ، Mina padhi. وإليك حاكمت ، Mina padhi. فاغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت ، Mina padhi. وأسررت وأعلنت ، Mina padhi. أنت إلهي لا إله لي غيرك ''aey Allah ! terey hi liye tareef hai to aasman w zameen ka Malik hai, hamd terey liye hi hai to aasman w zameen ka qaaim karne wala hai aur un sab ka jo usmein hain. teri hi liye hamd hai to aasman w zameen ka noor hai. tera qaul haq hai aur tera wada sach hai aur teri mulaqat sach aur jannat sach aur dozakh sach hai aur qiyamat sach hai. aey Allaah! maine terey hi samney sar jhukaa diya, main tujh hi par eman laayaa, maine terey hi uper bharosa kya aur teri hi taraf rujoo kya. maine teri hi madad ke sath muqaabla kya aur main tujhii se insaf ka talabgaar hun. to to meri maghfirat kar, un tamam gunahon mein jo main pahley kar chuka hun aur jo baad mein mujh se saadir hon jo maine chipa rakhey hain aur jinka maine izhar kya hai, to hi mera maabood hai aur terey siwa aur koi maabood nahi. ''aur ham se Sabit bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya aur kaha ke ham se Sufiyan Sory ne phir yahi hadis bayan ki aur is mein yun hai) أنت الحق وقولك الحق‏ . Mina (ke '' to haq hai aur tera kalam haq hai.''"
7386,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they aur jab ham bulandi par chadhtey to (zor se chilla kar) takbeer kehtey. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logo! apne uper raham khaao ! Allah bahraa nahi hai aur na wo kahin door hai. tum aik bahut sunney, bahut jaankaar aur qareeb rehney wali zaat ko bulatey ho. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas aaey. main us waqt dil main لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله keh raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya '' Abdullah-bin-Qais ! لا حول wla قوة إلا بالله kahaa karo ke ye jannat ke khazaanon mein se aik khazaana hai.'' ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya main tumhen ye na bata dun."
7387,"Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : ya Rasulullah! mujhey aisi dua sikhaaiye jo main apni Namaz mein kya karun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye padha karo اللهم إني zulmat نفسي ظلما كثيرا ، Mina padhi. wla يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت ، Mina padhi. فاغفر لي من عندك مغفرة ، Mina padhi. إنك أنت الغفور الرحيم‏''aey Allah ! maine apni jaan par bahut zulm kya aur terey siwa gunahon ko aur koi nahi bakhshtaa, to mere gunah apne paas se bakhsh de, bila shubah to bada maghfirat karne waalaa, bada raham karne wala hai.''"
7388,"abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : ya Rasulullah! mujhey aisi dua sikhaaiye jo main apni Namaz mein kya karun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye padha karo اللهم إني zulmat نفسي ظلما كثيرا ، Mina padhi. wla يغفر الذنوب إلا أنت ، Mina padhi. فاغفر لي من عندك مغفرة ، Mina padhi. إنك أنت الغفور الرحيم‏''aey Allah ! maine apni jaan par bahut zulm kya aur terey siwa gunahon ko aur koi nahi bakhshtaa, to mere gunah apne paas se bakhsh de, bila shubah to bada maghfirat karne waalaa, bada raham karne wala hai.''"
7389,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) ne mujhey pukar kar kaha ke Allah ne aap ki qaum ki baat sun li aur wo bhi sun liya jo unhon-ne aapko jawab diyaa.''
7390,"mujhey Jabir-bin-Abdullah Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba ko har jaayez kaam mein istikhaara karna sikhatey they jis tarah aap Quran ki sura sikhatey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke jab tum mein se koi kisi kaam ka irada karey to usey chahiye ke farz ke siwa 2 rakaat nafl Namaz padhey, phir salam ke baad ye dua karey ''aey Allah ! main terey ilm ke Tufail us kaam mein khairiyat talab karta hun aur teri qudrat ke Tufail taqat mangta hun aur tera fazal. kyonke tujhey qudrat hai aur mujhey nahi, to janta hai aur main nahi janta aur to ghaibon ka bahut jaanney wala hai. aey Allah ! to agar to ye baat janta hai (is waqt istikhaara karne waley ko us kaam ka naam lena chahiye (ke is kaam mein mere liye duniya w aakhirat mein bhalai hai ya is tarah farmaya ke ''mere Deen main aur guzraan main aur mere har anjam ke eitibaar se bhalai hai to is par mujhey qaadir bana de aur mere liye usey aasan kar de, phir usmein mere liye barkat ata farmaa. aey Allaah! aur agar to janta hai ke ye kaam mere liye bura hai. mere Deen aur guzaara ke eitibaar se aur mere anjam ke eitibaar se, ya farmaya ke meri duniya w Deen ke eitibaar se to mujhey us kaam se door kar de aur mere liye bhalai muqaddar kar de jahan bhi wo ho aur phir mujhey is par razi aur khush rakh."
7391,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qism is tarah khaatey ''qasam uski jo dilon ka pher dene wala hai.''
7392,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ke ninyaanwe naam hain, jo unhein yad kar lega wo jannat mein jaaeyga.''"
7393,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs apne bistar par jaey to usey chahiye ke usey apne kapdey ke kinarey se teen martaba saaf kar ley aur ye dua padhey باسمك رب وضعت جنبي وبك أرفعه ، Mina padhi. إن أمسكت نفسي فاغفر لها ، Mina padhi. وإن أرسلتها فاحفظها بما تحفظ به عبادك الصالحين ''aey mere rab! tera naam lekar main apni karwat rakhta hun aur terey naam hi ke sath usey uthaaoonga. agar tu ney meri jaan ko baqi rakha to usey maaf karna aur agar usey (apni taraf sotey hi mein) utha liya to uski hifazat is tarah karna jis tarah to apne neku-kaar bandon ki hifazat karta hai.'' is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Yahya aur Bishr bin Fazal ne Ubaidullah se ki hai, unse Saeed ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur zuhair, abu-Zamra aur Ismail bin Zakariya ne Ubaidullah se ye izafa kya ke unse Saeed ne, unse unke walid ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur uski riwayat ibne- Ajlan ne ki, unse Saeed ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne. uski mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman darawardi aur Usama bin Hafs ne ki."
7394,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab apne bistar par letney jatey to ye dua kartey ( اللهم باسمك أحيا وأموت )''aey Allah ! terey naam ke sath zinda hun aur usi ke sath maroonga . ''aur jab subah hoti to ye dua kartey الحمد لله الذي أحيانا بعد ما أماتنا وإليه النشور ''tamaam tareef us Allah ke liye hai jisne iske baad zinda kya ke ham mar chukey they aur usi ki taraf uth kar jana hai.''
7395,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat mein letney jatey to kehtey (باسمك نموت ونحيا ( ''ham terey hi naam se marengey aur usi se zinda hongey. ''aur jab bedaar hotey to kehtey الحمد لله الذي أحيانا بعد ما أماتنا وإليه النشور '' tamam tareef us Allah ke liye hai jisne hamein maarney ke baad zinda kya aur usi ki taraf jana hai.''
7396,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ''jab tum mein se koi apni biwi ke paas janey ka irada karey aur ye dua padh ley ( باسم الله , Mina اللهم جنبنا الشيطان , Mina وجنب الشيطان ما رزقتنا‏) '' shuru Allah ke naam se, aey Allaah! hamein shaitan se door rakhna aur to jo hamein bachcha ata karey usey bhi shaitan se door rakhnaa.'' to agar isi sohbat mein un donon se koi bachcha naseeb hua to shaitan usey kabhi nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega.''"
7397,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke main apne sadhaaey huey kuttey ko shikar ke liye chhorta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum sadhaaey huey kuttey chhodo aur unke sath Allah ka naam bhi ley lo, phir wo koi shikar pakdein aur usey khaaein nahi to tum usey kha saktey ho aur jab shikar par bin phaal ke teer yani lakdi se koi shikar maarey lekin wo nauk se lag kar janwar ka gosht cheer de to aisa shikar bhi khaao."
7398,unse Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke logon ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! wahan ke qabeeley abhi haal hi mein Islam laey aur wo hamein gosht la kar detey hain. hamein yaqin nahi hota ke zabah kartey waqt unhon-ne Allah ka naam bhi liya tha ya nahi (to kya ham usey kha saktey hain?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum is par Allah ka naam lekar usey kha liya karo. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman darawardi aur Usama bin Hafs ne ki.
7399,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 mendhon ki qurbani ki aur zabah kartey waqt bismillaahi-Allahu-akbar padha .
7400,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Zil-Hijja ki dasween taareekh ko maujood they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhai phir khutba diya aur farmaya ''jisne Namaz se pahley janwar zabah kar liya to uski jagah doosra janwar zabah karey aur jisne zabah abhi na kya ho to wo Allah ka naam lekar zabah kare.''
7401,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''apne bap daadon ki qism na khaya karo, agar kisi ko qism khaani hi ho to Allah ke naam ki qism khaaey warna khamosh rahe.''"
7402,"jo bani zohra ke haleef they aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon mein they ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Azl aur qaara walon ki darkhaast par das akaabir sahaba ko jin mein Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, unke yahan bhejaa. ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujhey Ubaidullah bin ayaaz ne khabar di ke Haris ki sahibzadi Zenab ne unhein bataya ke jab log Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko qatl karne ke liye aamada huey (aur qaid mein they) to usi zamaney mein unhon-ne unse safaaii karne ke liye ustra liya tha, jab wo log Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko haram se bahar qatl karne le gaey to unhon-ne ye ashaar kahey . ''aur jab main musalman honey ki haalat mein qatl kya ja raha hun to mujhey uski parwaa nahi ke mujhey kis pahlu par qatl kya jaeyga aur mera ye marnaa Allah ke liye hai aur agar wo chaahega to mere tukdey tukdey kiye huey aaza par barkat nazil karega .'' phir ibne- al-Haaris ne unhein qatl kar diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba ko us haadisa ki itlaa isi din di jis din ye hazraat Shahid kiye gaey they."
7403,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii bhi Allah se zyada ghairat mand nahi aur isi liye us ne fawaahish ko haram qarar diya hai aur Allah se zyada koi tareef pasand karne wala nahi. ''
7404,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Allah Taala ne makhlooq ko paida kya to apni kitab mein usey likhaa, us ne apni zaat ke mutaalliq bhi likha aur ye ab bhi arsh par likha hua maujood hai إن رحمتي تغلب غضبي ke ''meri rehmat mere ghazab par ghalib hai.''"
7405,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke main apne bandey ke guman ke sath hun aur jab wo mujhey apne dil mein yad karta hai to main bhi usey apne dil mein yad karta hun aur jab wo mujhey majlis mein yad karta hai to main usey us se behtar farishton ki majlis mein usey yad karta hun aur agar wo mujh se aik baalisht qareeb aata hai to main us se aik hath qareeb ho jata hun aur agar wo mujh se aik hath qareeb aata hai to main us se 2 hath qareeb ho jata hun aur agar wo meri taraf chal kar aata hai to main uske paas daud kar aa jata hoon.''
7406,jab ye aayat nazil huii قل هو القادر على أن يبعث عليكم عذابا من فوقكم''aap keh dijiye ke wo qaadir hai is par ke tum par tumharey uper se azab nazil kare.'' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha ''main terey munh ki panah mangta hoon.'' phir aayat ke ye alfaz nazil huey أو من تحت أرجلكم ''wo tumharey uper se tum par azab nazil karey ya tumharey paon ke nichey se azab aa jaaey.'' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir ye dua ki ke main terey munh ki panah chahta hun. phir ye aayat nazil hui ( أو يلبسكم شيعا‏ ( '' ya tumhen firqa bandi mein mubtala kar de (ke ye bhi azab ki qism hai) '' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aasan hai b-nisbat agley azaabon ke.
7407,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas dajjal ka zikr hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen achi tarah malum hai ke Allah kaana nahi hai aur aap ne hath se apni aankh ki taraf ishara kya aur dajjal Masih ki daain aankh kaani hogi, jaisey uski aankh par angoor ka aik utha hua daana ho."
7408,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne jitney Nabi bhejey un sab ne jhootey kaaney dajjal se apni qaum ko daraayaa, wo dajjal kaana hoga aur tumhara rab (aankhon wala hai) kaana nahi hai, us dajjal ki donon aankhon ke darmyan likha hua hoga (lafz) kaafir.''"
7409,"jang banu-mustaliq mein unhein baandiyaan ghaneemat mein miliin to unhon-ne chaha ke unse ham-bistarii karein lekin hamal na thahrey . chunanche logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se azl ke mutaalliq puchha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum azl bhi karo to koi qabahat nahi magar qiyamat tak jis jaan ke mutaalliq Allah Taala ne paida hona likh diya hai wo zaroor paida ho kar rahegi (is liye tumhara azl karna bekaar hai. maujooda jabrii nasl bandi ka jawaz us se nikaalnaa bilkul ghalat hai. aur Mujahid ne Qaza se bayan kya ke unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi bhi jaan jo paida honii hai, Allah Taala zaroor usey paida karke rahega."
7410,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala qiyamat ke din isi tarah jaisey ham duniya mein jama hotey hain, mominon ko ikattha karega (wo garmi wghaira se pareshan ho kar) kahengey kash! ham kisi ki sifarish apne Malik ke paas ley jatey taake hamein apni is haalat se aaraam miltaa. chunanche sab mil kar Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey. unse kahengey Adam ! aap logon ka haal nahi dekhtey kis bula mein giraftaar hain. aapko Allah Taala ne ( khas ( apne hath se banaya aur farishton se aapko sajda karaya aur har cheez ke naam aapko batlaaiye (har lughat mein bolnaa baat karna sikhlaayaa) kuchh sifarish kijiye taake ham logon ko is jagah se nijat ho kar aaraam miley. kahengey mein is laaiq nahi, unko wo gunah yad aa jaeyga jo unhon-ne kya tha ( mamnoo darakht mein se khana ( . (wo kahengey ( magar tum log aisa karo Nuh (Alaihissalam) paighambar ke paas jao wo pahley paighambar hain jinko Allah Taala ne zameen walon ki taraf bheja tha. aakhir wo log sab Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey, wo bhi yahi jawab dengey, main us laaiq nahi apni khata jo unhon-ne ( duniya mein) ki thi yad karengey. kahengey tum log aisa karo paighambar Ibrahim ke paas jao jo Allah ke khaleel hain ( log unke paas jaeinge ( wo bhi apni khataein yad karke kahengey main is laaiq nahi tum Musa (Alaihissalam) paighambar ke paas jao Allah ne unko Taurait inayat farmai, unse bol kar baatein kin. ye log Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey wo bhi yahi kahengey mein is laaiq nahi apni khata jo unhon-ne duniya mein ki thi yad karengey magar tum aisa karo Esa (Alaihissalam) paighambar ke paas jao wo Allah ke bandey, uske rasool, uske khas kalima aur khas Rooh hain. ye log Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey wo kahengey main is laaiq nahi tum aisa karo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao wo Allah ke aisey bandey hain jinki agli pichhli khataein sab bakhsh di gaee hain. aakhir ye sab log jama ho kar mere paas aaeingey. main chaloonga aur apne parwardigar ki bargah mein hazir honey ki ijazat maangonga , mujh ko ijazat milegii. main apne parwardigar ko dekhtey hi sajdey mein gir padoonga aur jab tak usko manzoor hai wo mujh ko sajdey hi mein padaa rehney dega. iske baad hukm hoga '' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar uthao aur arz karo tumhari arz suni jaeygi tumhari darkhaast manzoor hogi, tumhari sifarish maqbool hogi us waqt main apne Malik ki aisi aisii ta'reefein karunga jo wo mujh ko sikhaa chuka hai. (ya sikhlaaeyga) phir logon ki sifarish shuru kar doonga. sifarish ki aik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi. main unko jannat mein ley jaunga, phir lot kar apne parwardigar ke paas hazir hunga aur usko dekhtey hi sajdey mein gir padoon ga jab tak parwardigar chaahega mujh ko sajdey mein padaa rehney dega. iske baad irshad hoga '' Muhammad apna sar uthao jo tum kahogey suna jaeyga aur sifarish karogey to qabool hogi phir main apne parwardigar ki aisi ta'reefein karunga jo Allah ne mujh ko sikhlaayein (ya sikhlaaeyga) iske baad sifarish kar doonga lekin sifarish ki aik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi. main unko jannat mein ley jaaunga phir lot kar apne parwardigar ke paas hazir hunga usko dekhtey hi sajdey mein gir padoon ga jab tak parwardigar chaahega mujh ko sajdey mein padaa rehney dega. iske baad irshad hoga Muhammad apna sar uthao jo tum kahogey suna jaeyga aur sifarish karogey to qabool hogi phir main apne parwardigar ki aisi ta'reefein karunga jo Allah ne mujh ko sikhlaayein (ya sikhlaaeyga) iske baad sifarish shuru kar doonga lekin sifarish ki aik had muqarrar kar di jaeygi. mein unko bahisht mein ley jaaunga phir lot kar apne parwardigar ke paas hazir hoonga. arz karunga : ya paak parwardigaar! ab to dozakh mein aisey hi log reh gaey hain jo Quran ki wajah se dozakh hi mein hamesha rehney ke laaiq hain. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dozakh se wo log nikal liye jaeinge jinhoney (duniyaa mein) la ilaaha-illallaah kaha hoga aur unke dil mein aik jau barabar eman hoga phir wo log bhi nikal liye jaeinge jinhoney la ilaaha-illallaah kaha hoga aur unke dil mein gehun barabar eman hoga. ( gehun jau se chhota hota hai) phir wo bhi nikal liye jaeinge jinhoney la ilaaha-illallaah kaha hoga aur unke dil mein chewntii barabar (ya bhungey barabar ( eman hoga."
7411,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ka hath bharaa hua hai, usey raat din ki bakhshish bhi kam nahi karti , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tumhen malum hai ke jab us ne aasman w zameen paida kiye hain us ne kitna kharch kya hai us ne bhi usmein koi kami nahi paida ki jo iske hath mein hai aur farmaya ke uska arsh pani par hai aur uske doosrey hath mein taraazu hai, jisey wo jhukata aur uthata rehta hai."
7412,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din zameen uski muththii mein hogi aur aasman iske daahiney hath mein hoga, phir kahega ke main badshah hoon.'' uski riwayat Saeed ne Malik se ki."
7413,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah zameen ko apni muththii mein le-lega.''
7414,"aik Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad! Allah aasmanon ko aik ungli par rok lega aur zameen ko bhi aik ungli par aur pahadon ko aik ungli par aur darakhton ko aik ungli par aur makhlooqat ko aik ungli par, phir farmaeyga ke main badshah hun. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa diye yahan tak ke aap ke aagey ke dandaane-mubaarak dikhai dene lagey. phir sura Al-Anaam ki ye aayat padhii  وما قدروا الله حق قدره. Yahya-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya ke is riwayat mein Fuzel bin ayaaz ne Mansoor se izafa kya, unse Ibrahim ne, unse Ubeda ne, unse Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par tajjub ki wjah se aur uski tasdeeq kartey huey hans diye."
7415,"ahle-kitab mein se aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke aey abul-Qaasim ! Allah aasmanon ko aik ungli par rok lega , zameen ko aik ungli par rok lega, darakht aur mitti ko aik ungli par rok lega aur tamam makhlooqat ko aik ungli par rok lega aur phir farmaeyga ke main ''baadshaah hun, main badshah hoon'' maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap is par hans diye, yahan tak ke aap ke daant dikhai dene lagey, phir ye aayat padhii  وما قدروا الله حق قدره"
7416,"Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi ghair mard ko dekhun to seedhi talwaar se uski gardan mar dun phir ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tumhen Sad ki ghairat par hairat hai? bila shubah mein unse zyada ghairat mand hun aur Allah Taala mujh se zyada ghairat mand hai aur Allah ne ghairat hi ki wjah se fawaahish ko haram kya hai. chahey wo zahir mein hon ya chhup kar aur ma'zirat Allah se zyada kisi ko pasand nahi, isi liye us ne bashaarat dene waley aur daraane waley bhejey aur tareef Allah se zyada kisi ko pasand nahi, isi wjah se us ne jannat ka wada kya hai."
7417,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik sahib se puchha kya aapko Quran mein se kuchh cheez yad hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, falan-falan soortein unhon-ne unke naam bataaey ."
7418,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tha ke aap ke paas banu- Tameem ke kuchh log aaey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey banu- Tameem ! bashaarat qabool karo. unhon-ne is par kaha ke aap ne hamein bashaarat de di, ab hamein bakhshish bhi dijiye. phir aap ke paas Yaman ke kuchh log pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey ahal Yaman ! banu- Tameem ne bashaarat nahi qabool ki tum usey qabool karo. unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne qabool kar li. ham aap ke paas isliye hazir huey hain taake Deen ki samajh hasil karein aur taake aap se us duniya ki shuruaat ke mutaalliq poochhein ke kis tarah thi? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah tha aur koi cheez nahi thi aur Allah ka arsh pani par tha. phir us ne aasman w zameen paida kiye aur Lauhe-mahfooz mein har cheez likh di (Imraan bayan kartey hain ke) mujhey aik shakhs ne aa kar khabar di ke Imran apni ontni ki khabar lo wo bhag gaee hai. chunanche main uski talash mein nikla . maine dekha ke mere aur uske darmyan ret ka chatiyal maidan rukawat hai aur Allah ki qism meri tamanna thi ke wo chali hi gaee hoti aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein se na utha hota."
7419,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ka hath bharaa hua hai usey koi kharch kam nahi karta jo din w raat wo karta rehta hai kya tumhen malum hai ke jab se zameen w aasman ko us ne paida kya hai kitna kharch kar diya hai. us sarey kharch ne usmein koi kami nahi ki jo iske hath mein hai aur iska arsh pani par tha aur uske doosrey hath mein taraazu hai jisey wo uthata aur jhukata hai.
7420,Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) (apni biwi ki) shikayat karne lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah se daro aur apni biwi ko apne paas hi rakho . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi baat ko chhipaaney waley hotey to usey zaroor chhipaatey . bayan kya chunanche Zenab (Raziallahu anha) tamam paak beeviyon par fakhr se kehti thi ke tum logon ki tumharey ghar walon ne shadi ki. aur meri Allah Taala ne saat (7) aasmanon ke uper se shadi ki aur Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke aayat ( وتخفي في نفسك ما الله مبديه وتخشى Naas ( ''aur aap us cheez ko apne dil mein chhipaatey hain jisey Allah zahir karne wala hai.'' Zenab aur Zaid-bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein nazil hui thi.
7421,parde ki aayat Ummul-Momenin Zenab bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein nazil hui aur us din aap ne roti aur gosht ke waleeme ki dawat di aur Zenab (Raziallahu anha) tamam paak beeviyon par fakhr kya karti thin aur kehti thin ke mera nikah Allah ne aasman par karaya tha.
7422,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne jab makhlooq paida ki to arsh ke uper apne paas likh diya ke meri rehmat mere ghusse se badh kar hai.''
7423,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo Allah aur uske rasool par eman laya , Namaz qaaim ki, Ramazan ke rozey rakhey to Allah par haq hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil kare. chahe us ne hijrat ki ho ya wahin muqeem raha ho jahan uski paidaaish hui thii.'' sahaba ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kya ham iski itlaa logon ko na de dein ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat mein so darjey hain jinhein Allah Taala ne apne rastey mein jihad karne walon ke liye taiyaar kya hai, har 2 darjon ke darmyan itna fasla hai jitna aasman w zameen ke darmyan hai. to jab tum Allah se sawal karo to firdaus ka sawal karo kyonke wo darmyaana darjey ki jannat hai aur buland tareen aur uske uper Rehman ka arsh hai aur usi se jannat ki nehrein nikalti hain."
7424,"mein masjid mein dakhil hua aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they, phir jab suraj ghurub hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abu-Zar ! kya tumhen malum hai ye kahan jata hai? '' bayan kya ke maine arz kya ke Allah aur uska rasool zyada jaanney waley hain. farmaya ke ye jata hai aur sajda ki ijazat chahta hai phir usey ijazat di jati hai aur maano us se kaha jata hai ke wapas wahan jao jahan se aaey ho. chunanche wo maghrib ki taraf se tuloo hota hai, phir aap ne ye aayat padhii ذلك مستقر لها‏ Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat yun hi hai."
7425,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bula bhejaa, phir maine Quran ki talash ki aur sura Tauba ki aakhiri aayat abu-Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas paaii. ye aayatein mujhey kisi aur ke paas nahi mili thiin لقد جاءكم رسول من أنفسكم‏ sura Bara't (Tauba) ke aakhir tak. ham se Yahya-bin-Bukair ne bayan kya, unse Leis ne bayan kya aur unse Yunus ne yahi bayan kya ke abu-Khuzaima Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas sura tauba ki aakhiri aayatein paaein."
7426,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pareshani ke waqt ye dua kartey they لا إله إلا الله العليم الحليم لا إله إلا الله رب العرش العظيم لا إله إلا الله رب السموات ورب الأرض رب العرش الكريم''Allaah ke siwa koi maabood nahi jo bahut jaanney wala bada burdbaar hai, Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi jo arshe-azeem ka rab hai, Allah ke siwa koi rab nahi jo aasmanon ka rab hai, zameen ka rab hai aur arsh Karim ka rab hai.''"
7427,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din sab log behosh kar diye jaeinge phir main sabse pahley hosh mein aa kar Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekhoonga ke wo arsh ka aik paya pakdey khadey hongey.''
7428,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir main sabse pahley uthney wala hunga aur dekhoonga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ka paaya thaamey huey hain.''
7429,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ek ke baad doosrey tumharey paas raat aur din ke Farishtey aatey rahtey hain aur ye Asr aur fajr ki Namaz mein jama hotey hain, phir wo uper chadhtey hain, jinhoney raat tumharey sath guzari hoti hai. phir Allah tumharey barey mein unse poochhta hai halanke usey tumhari khub khabar hai, poochhta hai ke mere bandon ko tum ne kis haal mein chhodaa? wo kehtey hain ke ham ne us haal mein chhoda ke wo Namaz padh rahe they. ''"
7430,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne halal kamaaii se aik khajoor ke barabar bhi khairat ki aur Allah tak halal kamaaii hi ki khairat pahunchti hai, to Allah usey apne daain hath se qabool kar leta hai aur khairat karne waley ke liye usey is tarah badhata rehta hai jaisey koi tum mein se apne bachchey ki parwarish karta hai, yahan tak ke wo pahaad barabar ho jati hai.'' aur Warqaa ne is hadis ko Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat kya, unhon-ne Saeed bin Yasar se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, usmein bhi ye fiqra hai ke Allah ki taraf wahi khairat chadhtii hai jo halal kamaaii mein se ho."
7431,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua pareshani ke waqt kartey they لا إله إلا الله العظيم الحليم ، Mina padhi. لا إله إلا الله رب العرش العظيم ، Mina padhi. لا إله إلا الله رب السموات ورب العرش الكريم''koii maabood Allah ke siwa nahi jo azeem hai aur burdbaar hai, koi maabood Allah ke siwa nahi jo arshe-azeem ka rab hai, koi maabood Allah ke siwa nahi jo aasmanon ka rab hai aur arshe-kareem ka rab hai."
7432,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh sona bheja gaya to aap ne usey char aadmiyon mein taqseem kar diya aur mujh se Ishaq bin Nasar ne bayan kya, unse Abdur-Razzaq ne bayan kya, unhein Sufiyan ne khabar di, unhein unke walid ne, unhein ibne-abii-Nu'am ne aur unse Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Yaman se kuchh sona Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey Aqra-bin-Habis hanzalii, Uena bin Badri fazaarii, Alqama-bin-Ulaasa Aamiri aur Zaid al-taaii mein taqseem kar diya. is par Quraish aur Ansar ko ghussa aa gaya aur unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Najad ke raeeson ko to detey hain aur hamein chhod detey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik maslihat ke liye unka dil bahalaataa hun. phir aik shakhs jiski aankhen dhansii hui thin, peshani ubhrii hui thi, dadhi ghanii thi, donon kalley phooley huey they aur sar gathaa hua tha. us mardood ne kaha : aey Muhammad! Allah se dar. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar main bhi us (Allaah) ki nafarmani karunga to phir kon uski itaat karega? usne mujhey zameen par ameen banaya hai aur tum mujhey ameen nahi samajhtey. phir haaziriin mein se aik sahabi Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ya umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske qatl ki ijazat chahi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, phir jab wo janey laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shakhs ki nasl se aisey log paida hongey jo Quran ke sirf lafz padhengey lekin Quran unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega, wo Islam se is tarah nikal kar phenk diye jaeinge jis tarah teer shikaarii janwar mein se paar nikal jata hai, wo ahale-Islaam ko (kaafir keh kar) qatl karein aur but paraston ko chhod dengey agar maine unka daur paya to unhein qaume-aad ki tarah neest w naabood kar doonga ."
7433,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aayat ( والشمس تجري لمستقر لها‏ (ke mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska mustaqar arsh ke nichey hai.
7434,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey they ke aap ne chaand ki taraf dekha, chaudhawiin raat ka chaand tha aur farmaya ke tum log apne rab ko isi tarah dekhogey jis tarah is chaand ko dekh rahe ho aur uske dekhney mein koi dhakkam-peil nahi hogi. to agar tumhen iski taqat ho ke suraj tuloo honey ke pahley aur suraj ghurub honey ke baad ki namazon mein sustii na ho to aisa kar lo."
7435,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne rab ko saaf-saaf dekhogey.
7436,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaudahwiin raat ko hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke tum apne rab ko qiyamat ke din is tarah dekhogey jis tarah is chaand ko dekh rahe ho. iske dekhney mein koi rukawat nahi hogi. khullam-khullaa dekhogey, be-takalluf, be-mashaqqat, be-zahmat."
7437,"logon ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! kya ham qiyamat ke din apne rab ko dekhengey ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne poochha, kya chaudahwiin raat ka chaand dekhney mein koi dushwari hoti hai? logon ne arz kya nahi ya Rasulullah ! phir aap ne puchha kya jab badal na hon to tumhen suraj ko dekhney mein koi dushwari hoti hai? logon ne kaha nahi ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum isi tarah Allah Taala ko dekhogey qiyamat ke din Allah Taala logon ko jama karega aur farmaeyga ke tum mein jo koi jis cheez ki puja paat kya karta tha wo uske peechhey lag jaey. chunanche jo suraj ki puja karta tha wo suraj ke peechhey ho jaeyga jo chaand ki puja karta tha wo chaand ke peechhey ho jaeyga aur jo buton ki puja karta tha wo buton ke peechhey lag jaeyga (usi tarah qabron, ta'ziyon ke pujaarii qabron, ta'ziyon ke peechhey lag jaaeinge) phir ye ummat baqi reh jaeygi usmein badey darja ke shafaat karne waley bhi hongey ya munafiq bhi hongey Ibrahim ko un lafzon mein shak tha. phir Allah unke paas aayega aur farmaeyga ke main tumhara rab hun, wo jawab dengey ke ham yahin rahengey. yahan tak ke hamara rab aa jaey, jab hamara rab aa jaeyga to ham usey pehchan lengey. chunanche Allah Taala unke paas is sura mein aayega jisey wo pehchantey hongey aur farmaeyga ke main tumhara rab hun, wo iqrar karengey ke to hamara rab hai. chunanche wo uske peechhey ho jaeinge aur dozakh ki peeth par pul siraat nasab kar diya jaeyga aur main aur meri ummat sabse pahley usko paar karne waley hongey aur us din sirf anbiya baat kar sakengey aur anbiya ki zaban par ye hoga. aey Allaah! mujh ko mehfooz rakh, mujh ko mehfooz rakh aur dozakh mein darakht Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah aankdey hongey. kya tum ne Sadan dekha hai? logon ne jawab diya ke ji haan, ya Rasulullah! to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo Sadan ke kaanton hi ki tarah hongey albatta wo itney badey hongey ke iska tool w arz Allah ke siwa aur kisi ko malum na hoga. wo logon ko unke aamaal ke badley mein uchak lengey to unmein se kuchh wo hongey jo tabah hone-waale hongey aur apne burey amal ki wjah se wo dozakh mein gir jaeinge ya apne amal ke sath bandhey hongey aur unmein kuchh tukdey kar diye jaeinge ya badla diye jaeinge ya usi jaisey alfaz bayan kiye. phir Allah Taala tajallii farmaeyga aur jab bandon ke darmyan faisla karke farigh hoga aur dozkhiyon mein se jisey apni rehmat se bahar nikaalnaa chaahega to farishton ko hukm dega ke jo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thehratey they unhein dozakh se bahar nikaalein, ye wo log hongey jin par Allah Taala raham karna chaahega. unmein se jinhoney kalima la ilaaha-illallaah ka iqrar kya tha. chunanche Farishtey unhein sajdon ke nishan se dozakh mein pahchaanengey. dozakh ibne-Aadam ka har uzu (ang) jalaa kar bhasm kar degi siwa sajde ke nishan ke , kyonke Allah Taala ne dozakh par haram kya hai ke wo sajdon ke nishan ko jalaaey (ya Allaah! ham gunahgaaron ko dozakh se mehfooz rakhiyo ham ko teri rehmat se yahi ummeed hai) chunanche ye log dozakh se is haal mein nikaley jaeinge ke ye jal-bhun chukey hongey. phir un par aabe-hayaat daala jaeyga aur ye uske nichey se is tarah ug kar niklengey jis tarah sailaab ke koode karkat se sabza ug aata hai. phir Allah Taala bandon ke darmyan faisle se farigh hoga. aik shakhs baqi reh jaeyga jiska chehra dozakh ki taraf hoga, wo un dozkhiyon mein sabse aakhiri insan hoga jisey jannat mein dakhil hona hai. wo kahega : aey rab! mera munh dozakh se pher de kyonke mujhey uski garm hua ne pareshan kar rakha hai aur uski tezi ne jhulsaa daala hai. phir Allah Taala se wo us waqt tak dua karta rahega jab tak Allah chaahega . phir Allah Taala farmaeyga kya agar main tera ye sawal pura kar doonga to too mujh se kuchh aur maangega? wo kahega nahi, teri izzat ki qasam! iske siwa aur koi cheez nahi maangonga aur wo shakhs Allah rabbul-izzat se badey ahad w paiman karega. chunanche Allah uska munh dozakh ki taraf se pher dega. phir jab wo jannat ki taraf rukh karega aur usey dekhega to itni der khamosh rahega jitni der Allah Taala usey khamosh rehney dena chaahega. phir wo kahega : aey rab! mujhey sirf jannat ke darwazey tak pahuncha de. Allah Taala farmaeyga kya tu ney wada nahi kya tha ke jo kuchh maine diya hai uske siwa aur kuchh kabhi to nahi maangega? afsos ibne-Aadam to kitna wada khilaf hai. phir wo kahega: aey rab! aur Allah se dua karega. aakhir Allah Taala poochhega kya agar maine tera ye sawal pura kar diya to iske siwa kuchh aur maangega? wo kahega teri izzat ki qasam! iske siwa aur kuchh nahi maangon ga aur jitney Allah chaahega wo shakhs wada karega. chunanche usey jannat ke darwazey tak pahuncha dega. phir jab wo jannat ke darwazey par khada ho jaeyga to jannat usey samney nazar aaeygii aur dekhega ke iske andar kis qadr khairiyat aur musarrat hai. iske baad Allah Taala jitni der chaahega wo shakhs khamosh rahega. phir kahega : aey rab! mujhey jannat mein pahuncha de. Allah Taala is par kahega kya tu ney wada nahi kya tha ke jo kuchh maine tujhey de diya hai iske siwa to aur kuchh nahi maangega. Allah Taala farmaeyga afsos! ibne-Aadam to kitna wada khilaf hai. wo kahega : aey rab! mujhey apni makhlooq mein sabse badh kar bad-bakht na banaa. chunanche wo musalsal dua karta rahega yahan tak ke Allah Taala uski duaon par hans dega, jab hans dega to iske mutaalliq kahega ke usey jannat mein dakhil kar do. jannat mein usey dakhil kar dega to us se farmaeyga ke apni aarzuein bayan kar, wo apni tamam aarzuein bayan kar dega. yahan tak ke Allah Taala usey yad dilaaeyga. wo kahega ke falan cheez, falan cheez, yahan tak ke uski aarzuein khatm ho jaeyngi to Allah Taala farmaeyga ke ye aarzuein aur unhi jaisi tumhen mileingii. اللھم ارزقنا"
7438,Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath maujood they. unki hadis ka koi hissey radd nahi kartey they. albatta jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah Taala kahega ke ''ye aur inhiin jaisi tumhen aur mileingii'' to Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke iske das guna mileingii aey abu-Huraira. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka yahi irshad yad hai ke ''ye aur inhiin jaisi aur'' is par Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine aap ka ye irshad yad kya hai ke ''tumhein ye sab cheezein mileingii aur us se das gunaa'' aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye shakhs jannat mein sabse aakhiri dakhil honey wala hoga.
7439,"ham ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kya ham qiyamat ke din apne rab ko dekhengey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya tum ko suraj aur chaand dekhney mein kuchh takleef hoti hai jabke aasman bhi saaf ho? ham ne kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir apne rab ke deedaar main tumhen koi takleef nahi pesh aaeygii jis tarah suraj aur chaand ko dekhney mein nahi pesh aatii. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik awaz dene wala awaz dega ke har qaum iske sath jaey jiski wo puja kya karti thi. chunanche saleeb ke pujaarii apni saleeb ke sath , buton ke pujaarii apne buton ke sath , tamam jhootey ma'boodon ke pujaarii apne jhootey ma'boodon ke sath chaley jaeinge aur sirf wo log baqi reh jaeinge jo khalis Allah ki ibadat karne waley they. unmein nek w bad donon qism ke musalmanon hongey aur ahle-kitab ke kuchh baqi bachi log bhi hongey. phir dozakh unke samney pesh ki jaeygi wo aisi chamakdaar hogi jaisey maidan ka ret hota hai. (jo door se pani malum hota hai) phir yahood se puchha jaeyga ke tum kis ki puja kartey they. wo kahengey ke ham Uzer ibnullaah ki puja kya kartey they. unhein jawab milega ke tum jhootey ho Allah ke na koi biwi hai aur na koi ladka . tum kya chahtey ho? wo kahengey ke ham pani peenaa chahtey hain ke hamein us se sairaab kya jaey. unse kaha jaeyga ke piyo wo us chamaktii ret ki taraf pani jaan kar chaleingey aur phir wo jahannam mein daal diye jaengey. phir nasara se kaha jaeyga ke tum kis ki puja kartey they? wo jawab dengey ke ham Masih ibnullaah ki puja kartey they. unse kaha jaeyga ke tum jhootey ho. Allah ke na biwi thi aur na koi bachcha, ab tum kya chahtey ho? wo kahengey ke ham chahtey hain ke pani se sairaab kiye jaaein. unse kaha jaeyga ke piyo (unko bhi us chamaktii ret ki taraf chalaayaa jaaeyga) aur unhein bhi jahannam mein daal diya jaeyga yahan tak ke wahi baqi reh jaeinge jo khalis Allah ki ibadat kartey they, nek w bad donon qism ke musalmaan, unse kaha jaeyga ke tum log kyon rukey huey ho jabke sab log ja chukey hain? wo kahengey ham duniya mein unse aisey waqt juda huey ke hamein unki duniyawi faaydon ke liye bahut zyada zarurat thi aur ham ne aik awaz dene waley ko suna hai ke har qaum iske sath ho jaey jiski wo ibadat karti thi aur ham apne rab ke muntazir hain. bayan kya ke phir Allah jabbaar unke samney is sura ke ilawa dusri sura mein aayega jis mein unhon-ne usey pehli martaba dekha hoga aur kahega ke main tumhara rab hoon! log kahengey ke to hi hamara rab hai aur us din anbiya ke siwa aur koi baat nahi karega. phir poochhega : kya tumhen uski koi nishani malum hai? wo kahengey ke) saaq . Mina ( pindlii , phir Allah Taala apni pindlii kholega aur har momin uske liye sajde mein gir jaeyga sirf wo log baqi reh jaeinge jo dikhawey aur shohrat ke liye usey sajda kartey they, wo bhi sajda karna chaahengey lekin unki peeth takhte ki tarah ho kar reh jaeygi. phir unhein pul par laya jaeyga ham ne puchha : ya Rasulullah ! pul kya cheez hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, wo aik phisalwaan girney ka maqam hai is par sansaniyaan hain, aankdey hain, chaudey chaudey kaantey hain, unke sar khamdaar Sadan ke kaanton ki tarah hain jo Najad ke mulk mein hotey hain. momin is par palak maarney ki tarah, bijli ki tarah, hawa ki tarah, tez raftaar ghodey aur sawari ki tarah guzar jaengey. unmein kuchh to sahi salamat nijat paaney waley hongey aur kuchh jahannam ki aag se jhulas kar bach nikalney waley hongey yahan tak ke aakhiri shakhs is par se ghisat'tey huey guzrega tum log aaj ke din apna haq leney ke liye jitna taqaza aur mutalba mujh se kartey ho us se zyada musalman log Allah se taqaza aur mutalba karengey aur jab wo dekhengey ke apne bhaiyon mein se unhein nijat mili hai to wo kahengey ke aey hamarey rab! hamarey bhai bhi hamarey sath Namaz padhtey they aur hamarey sath rozey rakhtey they aur hamarey sath doosrey ( nek ( aamaal kartey they ( unko bhi dozakh se nijat farma ( chunanche Allah Taala farmaeyga ke jao aur jiske dil mein aik ashrafii ke barabar bhi eman paogey usey dozakh se nikal lo aur Allah unke chehron ko dozakh par haram kar dega. chunanche wo aaeingey aur dekhengey ke kuchh ka to jahannam mein qadam aur aadhi pindlii jalii hui hai. chunanche jinhein wo pahchaanengey unhein dozakh se nikaalengey, phir wapas aaeingey aur Allah Taala unse farmaeyga ke jao aur jiske dil mein aadhi ashrafii ke barabar bhi eman ho usey bhi nikal laao. chunanche jinko wo pehchantey hongey unko nikaalengey. phir wo wapas aaeingey aur Allah Taala farmaeyga ke jao aur jiske dil mein zarra barabar eman ho usey bhi nikal laao. chunanche pahchaaney janey walon ko nikaalengey . abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke agar tum meri tasdeeq nahi kartey to ye aayat padho (إن الله لا يظلم مثقال ذرة وإن تك حسنة يضاعفها) ''Allaah taala zarra barabar bhi kisi par zulm nahi kartaa.'' agar neki hai to usey badhata hai. phir anbiya aur momineen aur Farishtey shafaat karengey aur parwardigar ka irshad hoga ke ab khas meri shafaat baqi reh gaee hai. chunanche Allah Taala dozakh se aik muththii bhar lega aur aisey logon ko nikaalega jo koila ho gaey hongey. phir wo jannat ke sirey par aik nehar mein daal diye jaeinge jisey nahare-aab-hayaat kaha jata hai aur ye log iske kinarey se is tarah ubhrengey jis tarah sailaab ke kode-karkat se sabza ubhar aata hai. tum ne ye manzar kisi chattaan ke ya kisi darakht ke kinarey dekha hoga to jis par dhoop padtii rehti hai wo sabzaa bharta hai aur jis par saaya hota hai wo safaid ubharta hai. phir wo is tarah niklengey jaisey motii chamaktaa hai. iske baad unki gardanon par mehar kar di jaeyngi (ke ye Allah ke aazad karda ghulam hain) aur unhein jannat mein dakhil kya jaeyga ahle-jannat unhein ( عتقاء الرحمن ( kahengey . unhein Allah ne bila amal ke jo unhon-ne kya ho aur bila khair ke jo unhoney kiye hon jannat mein dakhil kya hai. aur unse kaha jaeyga ke tumhen wo sab kuchh milega jo tum dekhtey ho aur itna hi aur bhi milega."
7440,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din mominon ko (garm maidan mein) rok diya jaeyga yahan tak ke uski wjah se wo ghamgeen ho jaeinge aur (salaah karke ( kahengey ke kash! koi hamarey rab se hamari shafaat karta ke hamein is haalat se nijat miltii . chunanche wo mil kar Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur kahengey ke aap insanon ke bap hain, Allah ne aapko apne hath se paida kya aur aapko jannat mein maqam ata kya, aapko sajda karne ka farishton ko hukm diya aur aapko har cheez ke naam sikhaaey. aap hamari shafaat apne rab ke huzoor mein karein taake hamein us haalat se nijat de. bayan kya ke Adam (Alaihissalam) kahengey ke main is laaiq nahi wo apni us ghalati ko yad karengey jo bawajud rokney ke darakht kha leney ki wjah se unse hui thi aur kahengey ke Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao kyonke wo pahley Nabi hain jinhein Allah Taala ne zameen walon ki taraf rasool bana kar bheja tha. chunanche log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey to wo bhi ye farmaaengey ke main is laaiq nahi aur apni is ghalati ko yad karengey jo baghair ilm ke Allah rabbul-izzat se sawal karke (apne betey ki bakhshish ke liye) unhon-ne ki thi aur kahengey ke Ibrahim ke paas jao jo Allah ke khaleel hain. bayan kya ke ham sab log Ibrahim ke paas aaeingey to wo bhi yahi uzr karengey ke main us laaiq nahi aur wo un teen baton ko yad karengey jin mein aap ne bazahir ghalat bayaanii ki thi aur kahengey ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao . wo aisey bandey hain jinhein Allah Taala ne Taurait di aur unse baat ki aur unko nazdeek karke unse sargoshi ki. bayan kya ke phir log Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey to wo bhi kahengey ke main is laaiq nahi hun aur wo ghalati yad karengey jo aik shakhs ko qatl karke unhon-ne ki thi. (wo kahengey ( albatta Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao wo Allah ke bandey, uske rasool, Allah ki Rooh aur uska kalima hain. chunanche log Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey. wo farmaaengey ke main is laaiq nahi hun tum log Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao . wo aisey bandey hain ke Allah ne unke agley pichhley tamam gunah maaf kar diye. chunanche log mere paas aaeingey aur main apne rab se uske dare-daulat yani arshe-muallaa par aaney ke liye ijazat chaahoonga. mujhey uski ijazat di jaeygi phir main Allah Taala ko dekhtey hi sajde mein gir padoonga aur Allah Taala mujhey jab tak chaahega usi haalat mein rehney dega. phir farmaeyga ke aey Muhammad ! sar uthao , kaho suna jaeyga, shafaat karo tumhari shafaat qabool ki jaeygi, jo maangogey diya jaeyga bayan kya ke phir main apna sar uthaaoonga aur apne rab ki hamd w sana karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaaey ga. bayan kya ke phir main shafaat karunga. chunanche mere liye had muqarrar ki jaeygi aur main iske mutabiq logon ko dozakh se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga. Qatada ne bayan kya ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke phir main nikalunga aur jahannam se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga. phir teesri martaba apne rab se uske dare-daulat ke liye ijazat chaahoonga aur mujhey uski ijazat di jaeygi. phir main Allah rabbul-izzat ko dekhtey hi uske liye sajde mein gir padoonga aur Allah Taala jab tak chaahega mujhey yun hi chhodey rakhega. phir farmaeyga : aey Muhammad! sar uthaao, kaho suna jaeyga shafaat karo qabool ki jaeygi, maango diya jaeyga aap ne bayan kya ke main apna sar uthaaoonga aur apne rab ki aisi hamd w sana karunga jo wo mujhey sikhaaeyga, bayan kya ke phir shafaat karunga aur mere liye had muqarrar kar di jaaeygi aur main iske mutabiq jahannam se logon ko nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga. Qatada ne bayan kya ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke phir main logon ko nikalunga aur unhein jahannam se nikal kar jannat mein dakhil karunga, yahan tak ke jahannam mein sirf wahi log baqi reh jaeinge jinhein Quran ne rok rakha hoga yani unhein hamesha hi usmein rehna hoga (yani kuffaar aur mushrekeen) phir aap ne ye aayat tilawat ki) عسى أن يبعثك ربك مقاما محمودا‏ ( '' qareeb hai ke aap ka rab maqam Mehmood par aapko bhejega'' farmaya ke yahi wo maqam Mehmood hai jiske liye Allah Taala ne apne Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wada kya hai."
7441,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko bula bheja aur unhein aik derey mein jama kya aur unse kaha ke sabr karo yahan tak ke tum Allah aur uske rasool se aa kar milo, main hauz par hoonga."
7442,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke waqt tahajjud ki Namaz mein ye dua kartey they (اللهم ربنا لك الحمد، Mina ‏‏‏‏أنت قيم السموات والأرض، Mina ‏‏‏‏ولك الحمد أنت رب السموات والأرض ومن فيهن، Mina ‏‏‏‏ولك الحمد أنت نور السموات والأرض ومن فيهن، Mina ‏‏‏‏أنت الحق، Mina ‏‏‏‏وقولك الحق، Mina ‏‏‏‏ووعدك الحق، Mina ‏‏‏‏ولقاؤك الحق، Mina ‏‏‏‏والجنة حق، Mina ‏‏‏‏والنار حق، Mina ‏‏‏‏والساعة حق، Mina ‏‏‏‏اللهم لك أسلمت، Mina padhi. وبك آمنت، Mina ‏‏‏‏وعليك توكلت، Mina ‏‏‏‏وإليك خاصمت، Mina ‏‏‏‏وبك حاكمت، Mina فاغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت، Mina ‏‏‏‏وأسررت وأعلنت، Mina ‏‏‏‏وما أنت أعلم به مني، Mina ‏‏‏‏لا إله إلا أنت) ''aey Allaah! aey hamarey rab! hamd terey hi liye hai, to aasman w zameen ka thamney wala hai aur un sab ka jo unmein hain aur terey hi liye hamd hai, to aasman w zameen ka noor hai aur un sab ka jo unmein hain. to sachcha hai, tera qaul sachchaa, tera wada sachchaa, teri mulaqat sachchii hai, jannat sach hai, dozakh sach hai, qiyamat sach hai. aey Allaah! main terey samney jhukaa, tujh par eman laayaa, tujh par bharosa kya, terey paas apne jhagdey ley gaya aur teri hi madad se muqaabla kya, to to mujhey maaf kar de, mere wo gunah bhi jo main pahley kar chuka hun aur wo bhi jo baad mein karunga aur wo bhi jo maine posheeda taur par kiye aur wo bhi jo zahir taur par kya aur wo bhi jin main to mujh se zyada janta hai. terey siwa aur koi maabood nahi. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Qais-bin-Sad aur abu-Zubair ne Taaus ke hawale se ( qiyam ( bayan kya aur Mujahid ne ( قيوم ( kaha yani har cheez ki nigrani karne wala aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( qiyam ( padha aur donon hi madah (taareef) ke liye hain."
7443,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein koi aisa nahi hoga jis se uska rab kalam na karey, iske aur bandey ke darmyan koi tarjuman na hoga aur na koi hijaab hoga jo usey chhipaaey rakhey.''"
7444,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''2 jannatein aisi hongi jo khud aur is mein Sara saman chandi ka hoga aur 2 jannatein aisi hongi jo khud aur uska Sara saman soney ka hoga aur jannate-adn mein qaum aur Allah ke deedaar ke darmyan sirf badai ki chadar rukawat hogi jo Allah rabbul-izzat ke munh par padi hogii.''
7445,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne kisi musalman ka maal jhooti qism kha kar mar liya to wo Allah se is haal mein milega ke wo is par ghazabnaak hoga.'' Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tasdeeq ke taur par Quran Majeed ki us aayat ki tilawat ki (إن الذين يشترون بعهد الله وأيمانهم ثمنا قليلا أولئك لا خلاق لهم في الآخرة wla يكلمهم الله‏)'' bila shubah jo log Allah ke ahad aur uski qasmon ko thodi poonjii ke badley bechtey hain yahi wo log hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahi aur Allah unse baat nahi karega.'' aakhir aayat tak.
7446,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' teen aadmi aisey hain jin se Allah Taala qiyamat ke din baat nahi karega aur na unki taraf rehmat se dekhega . aik wo jisne kisi saman ke mutaalliq qism khaaii ke usey us ne itney mein khareedaa hai, halanke wo jhoota hai. doosra wo shakhs jisne Asr ke baad jhooti qism isliye khaaii ke kisi musalman ka maal nahaq mar ley aur tesraa wo shakhs jisne zarurat se faaltu pani maangney waley ko nahi diya to Allah Taala qiyamat ke din us se kahega ke jis tarah tu ney us zarurat se zaayeda, faaltu cheez se doosrey ko rokaa jisey terey hathon ne banaya bhi nahi tha, main bhi tujhey apna Fazal nahi doonga ."
7447,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' zamana apni aslii puraanii shakl par ghoom kar aa gaya hai jis par Allah Taala ne zameen w aasman ko paida kya tha. saal baara mahiney ka hota hai jin mein char mahiney hurmat waley mahiney hain. teen musalsal yani Zi-Qaada , Zil-Hijja aur Muharram aur rajab Muzar jo jumaadiul-aakhir aur Shoban ke darmyan mein aata hai. phir aap ne puchha ke ye kon sa mahina hai? ham ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. aap khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha ke aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye Zil-Hijja nahi hai? ham ne kaha kyon nahi. phir farmaya ye kon sa Shahar hai? ham ne kaha Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai phir aap khamosh ho gaey aur ham ne samjha ke aap iska koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye paak Shahar Makka nahi hai? ham ne arz kya kyon nahi. phir farmaya ye kon sa din hai? ham ne arz kya Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. phir aap khamosh ho gaey ham ne samjha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska koi aur naam rakhengey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya ye yaumun-nahar (qurbaanii ka din) nahi hai? ham ne kaha kyon nahi phir farmaya ke phir tumhara khoon aur tumharey amwaal Muhammad ne bayan kya ke mujhey khayal hai ke ye bhi kaha ke aur tumhari izzat tum par isi tarah haram hain jaisey tumharey is din ka haram hona tumharey is Shahar aur is mahiney mein hai aur an-qareeb tum apne rab se milogey aur wo tumharey aamaal ke mutaalliq tum se sawal karega . aagah ho jao ke mere baad gumrah na ho jana ke aik doosrey ko qatl karne lago. aagah ho jaao! jo maujood hain wo ghair haaziron ko meri ye baat pahuncha dein. shayad koi jisey baat pahunchai gaee ho wo yahan sunney waley se zyada mehfooz rakhney wala ho. chunanche Muhammad-bin Sirin jab iska zikr kartey to kehtey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sach farmaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, haan kya maine pahuncha diya? haan! kya maine pahuncha diya?"
7448,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) (ka ladka jaan nikalney ke aalim mein tha to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bula bhejaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein kahlaayaa ke Allah hi ka wo hai jo wo leta hai aur wo bhi jisey wo deta hai aur sab ke liye aik muddat muqarrar hai, to sabr karo aur usey sawab ka kaam samjho . lekin unhon-ne phir dobara bula bheja aur qism dilai . chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey aur main bhi aap ke sath chala . Muaaz-bin-Jabal, Ubai-bin-Kab aur Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) bhi sath they. jab ham sahibzadi ke ghar mein dakhil huey to logon ne bachchey ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko god mein de diya. us waqt bachche ka saans ukhad raha tha. aisa malum hota tha jaisa puraanii mashk. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dekh kar ro diye to Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, aap rotey hain! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah apne bandon mein raham karne walon par hi raham khata hai."
7449,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat w dozakh ne apne rab ke huzoor mein jhagdaa kya. jannat ne kaha : aey rab! kya haal hai ke mujh mein kamzor aur girey padey log hi dakhil hongey aur dozakh ne kaha ke mujh main to daakhile ke liye mutakabbiron ko khas kar diya gaya hai. is par Allah Taala ne jannat se kaha ke to meri rehmat hai aur jahannam se kaha ke to mera azab hai. terey zariey mein jisey chahta hun usmein mubtala karta hun aur tum mein se har aik ki bhartii honey wali hai. kaha ke jahan tak jannat ka talluq hai to Allah apni makhlooq mein kisi par zulm nahi karega aur dozakh ki is tarah se ke Allah apni makhlooq mein se jis ko chaahega dozakh ke liye paida karega wo usmein dali jaeygi iske baad bhi dozakh kahegii aur kuchh makhlooq hai (main abhi khali hun) teen baar aisa hi hoga, aakhir parwardigar apna paon usmein rakh dega, us waqt wo bhar jaeygi, aik par aik ulat kar simat jaeygi, kehney lagegii bas bas-bas mein bhar gaee."
7450,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' kuchh log un gunahon ki wjah se jo unhon-ne kiye hongey, aag se jhulas jaeinge ye unki saza hogi. phir Allah apni rehmat se unhein jannat mein dakhil karega aur unhein jahannami kaha jaeyga aur Hammam ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
7451,"aik Yahudi aalim Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Muhammad! qiyamat ke din Allah Taala aasmanon ko aik ungli par, zameen ko aik ungli par, pahadon ko aik ungli par, darakht aur nehron ko aik ungli par aur tamam makhlooqat ko aik ungli par rakhega . phir apne hath se ishara karke kahega ke main hi badshah hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans diye aur ye aayat padhii (وما قدروا الله حق قدره) (jo sura الزمر mein hai)."
7452,"aik raat maine Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar guzari us raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhiin ke paas they. mera maqsad raat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz dekhnaa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne thodi der to apni ahliya ke sath baat cheet ki phir so gaey. jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey ya kuchh hissey baqi reh gaya to aap uth baithey aur aasman ki taraf dekh kar ye aayat padhii (إن في خلق السموات والأرض) ''bila shubah aasmanon aur zameen ki paidaaish mein aql rakhney walon ke liye nishaniyan hain ''phir uth kar aap ne wuzu kya aur miswak ki, phir gyara (11) rakatein padhin, phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz ke liye azan di aur aap ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir bahar aagey aur logon ko subah ki Namaz padhai."
7453,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Allah Taala makhlooq ko paida kar chuka to arsh ke uper apne paas ye likha ke meri rehmat mere ghusse se aagey badh gaee hai.
7454,"ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmaya jo sachchon ke sachey hain ke insan ka nutfa maa ke pet mein chalis (40) din aur raaton tak jama rehta hai phir wo khoon ki phutkii bin jata hai, phir wo gosht ka lothdaa ho jata hai phir uske baad farishta bheja jata hai aur usey char chizon ka hukm hota hai. chunanche wo uski rozii, uski maut, uska amal aur ye ke wo bad-bakht hai ya nek bakht likh leta hai. phir usmein Rooh phoonktaa hai aur tum mein se aik shakhs jannat walon ke se amal karta hai aur jab iske aur jannat ke darmyan sirf aik hath ka farq reh jata hai to uski taqdeer ghalib aati hai aur wo dozakh walon ke amal karne lagta hai aur dozakh mein dakhil hota hai. isi tarah aik shakhs dozakh walon ke amal karta hai aur jab uske aur dozakh ke darmyan sirf aik baalisht ka fasla reh jata hai to taqdeer ghalib aati hai aur jannat walon ke kaam karne lagta hai, phir jannat mein dakhil hota hai."
7455,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Jibraaiil! aapko hamarey paas us se zyada aaney mein kya rukawat hai jitna aap aatey rahtey hain? is par ye aayat nazil hui ( وما نتنزل إلا بأمر ربك له ما بين أيدينا وما خلفنا‏ ( ''aur ham nazil nahi hotey lekin aap ke rab ke hukm se, usi ka hai wo sab kuchh jo hamarey samney hai aur jo hamarey peechhey hai'' bayan kya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yahi jawab aayat mein utra ."
7456,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke aik khet mein ja raha tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik khajoor ki chhadi par teik laga letey they. phir aap yahudiyon ki aik jamat se guzrey to unmein se kuchh ne kuchh se kaha ke unse Rooh ke mutaalliq poochho aur kuchh ne kaha ke iske mutaalliq mat poochho. aakhir unhon-ne puchha to aap chhadi par tek laga kar khadey ho gaey aur main aap ke peechhey tha. maine samajh liya ke aap par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. chunanche aap ne ye aayat padhii ( ويسألونك an (an) الروح قل الروح من أمر ربي وما أوتيتم من العلم إلا قليلا ( ''aur log aap se Rooh ke mutaalliq poochhtey hain, keh dijiye ke Rooh mere rab ke Amr ( مٰن ( se aur tumhen ilm bahut thoda diya gaya hai.'' is par kuchh yahudiyon ne apne sathiyon se kaha ke ham ne kaha na tha ke mat poochho ."
7457,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs ne Allah ke raaste mein jihad kya aur uske liye nikalney ka maqsad uske rastey mein jihad aur uske kalam ki tasdeeq ke siwa aur kuchh nahi tha to Allah uska zaamin hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil karey (agar wo Shahid ho gaya) ya sawab aur maale-ghanimat ke sath usey wahin wapas lautaaey jahan se wo aaya tha.''
7458,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha ke koi shakhs hamiiyat ki wjah se ladtaa hai, koi bahaadurii ki wjah se ladtaa hai aur koi dikhawey ke liye ladtaa hai. to unmein se kon Allah ke rastey mein hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo isliye ladtaa hai ke Allah ka kalima hi buland rahe."
7459,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat mein se aik giroh dusron par ghalib rahega, yahan tak ke) أمر الله ( yani (qiyamat ( aa jaeygi."
7460,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat mein se aik giroh hamesha Quran w hadis par qaaim rahega, usey jhutlaaney waley aur mukhalifon koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakengey, yahan tak ke) أمر الله ( (qiyamat ( aa jaeygi aur wo usi haal mein hongey. is par Maalik-bin-Yukhaamir ne kaha ke maine Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke ye giroh Sham (Syria) mein hoga. is par Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha ke ye giroh Sham (Syria) mein hoga."
7461,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Musailma ke paas rukey, wo apne haamiyon ke sath Madina mein aaya tha aur us se farmaya ke agar to mujh se ye lakdi ka tukda bhi maangey to main ye bhi tujh ko nahi de sakta aur tumharey barey mein Allah ne jo hukm de rakha hai to us se aagey nahi badh sakta aur agar tu ney Islam se peeth pherii to Allah tujhey halaak kar dega."
7462,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke aik khet mein chal raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hath ki chhadi ka sahara letey jatey they, phir ham yahudiyon ki aik jamat ke paas se guzrey to un logon ne aapas mein kaha ke unse Rooh ke barey mein poochho . kuchh yahudiyon ne mashwara diya ke na poochho, kahin koi aisi baat na kahein jiska (unki zaban se sunnaa) tum pasand na karo. lekin kuchh ne israar kya ke nahin! ham poochhengey. chunanche unmein se aik ne uth kar kaha : aey abul-Qaasim! Rooh kya cheez hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par khamosh ho gaey. maine samajh liya ke aap par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhii ( ويسألونك an (an) الروح قل الروح من أمر ربي وما أوتوا من العلم إلا قليلا‏ ( ''aur log aap se Rooh ke barey mein poochhtey hain. keh dijiye ke Rooh mere rab ke Amr mein se hai aur tumhen iska ilm bahut thoda diya gaya hai.'' Aamash ne kaha ke hamari qirat mein isi tarah hai."
7463,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne Allah ke rastey mein jihad kya aur apne ghar se sirf is gharaz se nikla ke khalis Allah ke rastey mein jihad karey aur uske kalime tauheed ki tasdeeq karey to Allah Taala uski zamaanat ley leta hai ke usey jannat mein dakhil karega ya phir sawab aur ghaneemat ke sath iske ghar wapas karega.''
7464,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tum dua karo to azm ke sath karo aur koi dua mein ye na kahey ke agar to chahey to falan cheez mujhey ata kar, kyonke Allah se koi zabardastii karne wala nahi.''"
7465,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar raat mein tashrif laey aur unse kaha kya tum log Namaz tahajjud nahi padhtey . Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamari jaanein Allah ke hath mein hain, jab wo hamein uthana chaahega utha dega. jab maine ye baat kahi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas chaley gaey aur mujhey koi jawab nahi diya. albatta maine aapko wapas jatey waqt ye kehtey suna. aap apni raan par hath mar kar ye farma rahe they ( وكان الإنسان أكثر شىء جدلا‏ (ke '' insan bada hi bahas karne wala hai.''"
7466,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momin ki misal khet ke narm paudey ki si hai ke jidhar hawa chaltii hai to uske pattey udhar jhuk jatey hain aur jab hawa ruk jati hai to pattey bhi barabar ho jatey hain. isi tarah momin aazmaaishon mein bachaya jata hai lekin kaafir ki misal shamshaad ke sakht darakht jaisi hai ke aik haalat par khada rehta hai yahan tak ke Allah jab chahta hai usey ukhaad deta hai.''
7467,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par khadey farma rahe they ke tumhara zamana guzishta ummaton ke muqable mein aisa hai jaisey Asr se suraj doobney tak ka waqt hota hai. Taurait walon ko Taurait di gaee aur unhon-ne is par amal kya, yahan tak ke din aadha ho gaya. phir wo aajiz ho gaey to unhein uske badley mein aik qirat diya gaya. phir Injeel walon ko Injeel di gaee to unhon-ne is par Asr ki Namaz ke waqt tak amal kya aur phir wo amal se aajiz aagey to unhein bhi eik-eik qirat diya gaya. phir tumhen Quran diya gaya aur tum ne is par suraj doobney tak amal kya aur tumhen iske badley mein 2-2 qirat diye gaey. Taurait walon ne is par kaha ke aey hamarey rab! ye log musalman sabse kam kaam karne waley aur sabse zyada ajr paaney waley hain. Allah Taala ne is par farmaya ke kya maine tumhen ajr dene mein koi naa-insaafii ki hai? wo boley ke nahin! to Allah Taala farmaya ke ye to mera Fazal hai, main jis par chahta hun karta hun."
7468,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik jamat ke sath bait ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tum se is baat par bait leta hun ke tum Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraaogey, fuzool-kharchii nahi karogey, zina nahi karogey, apni aulad ko qatl nahi karogey aur man-ghadat bohtan kisi par nahi lagaaogey aur nek kaamon mein meri nafarmani nahi karogey. to tum mein se jo koi is ahad ko pura karega uska ajr Allah par hai aur jisne kahin khata ki aur usey duniya mein hi pakad liya gaya to ye had uske liye kaffara aur paakii bin jaeygi aur jiski Allah ne parda poshii ki to phir Allah par hai jisey chahey azab de aur jisey chahey uska gunah bakhsh de."
7469,Allah ke Nabi Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki sath (60) beeviyan thin to unhon-ne kaha ke aaj raat main tamam beeviyon ke paas jaaunga aur har biwi haamla hogi aur phir aisa bachcha janegi jo shehsawaar hoga aur Allah ke rastey mein ladega. chunanche wo apni tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey. lekin sirf aik biwi ke yahan bachcha paida hua aur wo bhi adhooraa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne inshaAllah keh diya hota to phir har biwi haamla hoti aur shehsawaar jannati jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad karta.
7470,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dehati ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif le gaey aur us se kaha ke koi muzaayqa nahi ye (beemaarii) tumharey liye paakii ka zaria'a hai, is par usne kaha ke janab ye wo bukhar hai jo aik buddhe par josh mar raha hai aur usey qabr tak pahuncha ke rahega , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir yoonhii hoga."
7471,"jab sab log soey aur Namaz qaza ho gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah tumhari ruhon ko jab chahta hai rok deta hai aur jab chahta hai chhod deta hai, to tum apni zarooraton se farigh ho kar wuzu karo, aakhir jab suraj poori tarah tuloo ho gaya aur khub din nikal aaya to aap khadey huey aur Namaz padhi."
7472,"aik musalman aur aik Yahudi ne aapas mein jhagdaa kya. musalman ne kaha ke us zaat ki qism jisne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tamam duniya mein chun liya aur Yahudi ne kaha ke us zaat ki qism jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam duniya mein chun liya is par musalman ne hath uthaya aur Yahudi ko tamaancha mar diya. Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur us ne apna aur musalman ka mamla aap se zikr kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Musa (Alaihissalam) par tarjeeh na do, tamam log qiyamat ke din pahlaa Saur phoonkney par behosh kar diye jaengey. phir doosra Saur phoonkney par main sabse pahley bedaar hunga lekin main dekhunga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ka aik kinara pakdey huey hain, ab mujhey malum nahi ke kya wo unmein they jinhein behosh kya gaya tha aur mujh se pahley hi unhein hosh aa gaya ya unhein Allah Taala ne ussey alag kar diya tha."
7473,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dajjal Madina tak aayega lekin dekhega ke farishta uski hifazat kar rahe hain to na to dajjal us se qareeb ho sakega aur na taaoon, agar Allah ne chaahaa.''"
7474,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har Nabi ki aik dua qabool hoti hai to main chahta hun agar Allah ne chaha ke apni dua qiyamat ke din apni ummat ki shafaat ke liye mehfooz rakhoon .''
7475,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine apne aapko aik kuwein par dekha. phir maine jitna Allah Taala ne chaha usmein se pani nikala . iske baad Abu-Bakar bin abi qahaafa (Raziallahu anhu) ne dol ley liya aur unhon-ne bhi aik 2 dol pani nikala albatta unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi aur Allah unhein maaf kare. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ley liya aur wo unke hath mein aik bada dol bin gaya. maine kisi qawii aur bahaadur ko is tarah dol par dol nikaaltey nahi dekha, yahan tak ke logon ne unke charon taraf maweshiyon ke liye baadein bana lein. ''"
7476,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas koi maangney wala aata ya koi zarurat mand aata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke uski sifarish karo taake tumhen bhi sawab miley, Allah apne rasool ki zaban par wahi jari karta hai jo chahta hai."
7477,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs is tarah dua na karey ke aey Allah ! agar to chahey to meri maghfirat kar, agar to chahey to mujh par raham kar, agar to chahey to mujhey rozii de, balke pukhtagi ke sath sawal karna chahiye kyonke Allah jo chahta hai karta hai koi is par jabr karne wala nahi. ''"
7478,"wo aur Hur-bin-Qais bin-haseen fazaarii, Musa (Alaihissalam) ke sathi ke barey mein ikhtilaf kar rahe they ke kya wo khizr (Alaihissalam) hi they. itney mein Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ka udhar se guzar hua aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bulaya aur unse kaha ke main aur mera ye sathi us barey mein shak mein hain ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ke wo sahib kon they jin se mulaqat ke liye Musa (Alaihissalam) ne rasta puchha tha. kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us silsile mein koi hadis suni hai unhon-ne kaha ke haan. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ke aik majme' mein they ke aik shakhs ne aa kar puchha kya aap kisi aisey shakhs ko jantey hain jo aap se zyada ilm rakhta ho? Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke nahi. chunanche aap par wahi nazil hui ke kyon nahi hamara banda khizr hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unse mulaqat ka rasta malum kya aur Allah Taala ne uske liye machhli ko nishan qarar diya aur aap se kaha gaya ke jab tum machhli ko gum paogey to lot jana ke wahin unse mulaqat hogi. chunanche Musa (Alaihissalam) machhli ka nishan dariya mein dhoondney lagey aur aap ke sathi ne aapko bataya ke aapko malum hai. jab ham ne chattaan par dera daala tha to wahin mein machhli bhool gaya aur mujhey shaitan ne usey bhulaa diya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke ye jagah wahi hai jiski talash mein ham sargardaan hain to wo donon apne qadmon ke nishaanon par wapas lautey aur unhon-ne khizr (Alaihissalam) ko pa liya un hi donon ka ye qissa hai jo Allah ne bayan farmaya,"
7479,"aap ne (hijjatul-wadaa ke mauqe par) farmaya ke ham kal insha-Allah khaif, banu- kinaana mein qiyam karengey jahan aik zamane mein kuffaar Makka ne kufr hi par qaaim rehney ki aapas mein qismein khaaein thin aap ki murad wadi Muhassab se thi."
7480,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Taaif walon ko gher liya, usko fateh nahi kya. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kal Allah ne chaha to ham Madina ko lot chalengey, is par musalman boley waah ham fateh kiye baghair lot jaaein, aap ne farmaya ke aisa hai to phir kal sawerey ladai shuru karo, subah ko musalman ladney lagey lekin (qila' fateh nahi hua) musalman zakhmi huey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke subah ko Allah ne chaha to ham Madina lot chalengey, is par musalman khush huey, musalmanon ka ye haal dekh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey."
7481,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Allah Taala aasman mein koi faisla karta hai to Farishtey uske farman ke aagey aajizii ka izhar karne ke liye apne bazu maartey hain (aur unse aisi awaz nikalti hai) jaisey patthar par zanjeer maari gaee ho. Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha Sufiyan ke siwa doosrey rawiyon ne is hadis mein bajaey (safwaan) ke) فاصفوان ( riwayat kya hai aur Abu-Sufiyan ne ( Safwan ( riwayat kya hai donon ke mana aik hi hain yani chiknaa saaf patthar aur ibne-aamir ne ( فزع ( padha hai, yani jab unke dilon ko faraghat hasil ho jati hai. matlab wahi hai ke dar jata raha hai phir wo hukm farishton mein aata hai aur jab unke dilon se khof door ho jata hai to wo poochhtey hain ke tumharey rab ne kya kahaa? jawab detey hain ke haq , Allah wo buland w azeem hai."
7482,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala kisi baat ko itna mutwajjeh ho kar nahi sunta jitna Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Quran padhna mutwajjeh ho kar sunta hai jo khush aawaazi se usko padhta hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik sathi ne kaha is hadis main ( يتغنى بالقرآن (ka ye mana hai ke usko pukar kar padhta hai.
7483,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmaeyga, aey Adam ! wo kahengey ( لبيك وسعديك‏ . Mina ( phir buland awaz se nidaa dega ke Allah tumhen hukm deta hai ke apni nasl mein se dozakh ka lashkar nikal .''"
7484,jis qadr mujhey Khadija (Raziallahu anha) par ghairat aati thi aur kisi aurat par nahi aati thi aur unke rab ne hukm diya tha ke unhein jannat mein aik ghar ki bashaarat de dein.
7485,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Allah Taala kisi bande se mohabbat karta hai to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko awaz deta hai ke Allah falan se mohabbat karta hai tum bhi us se mohabbat karo. chunanche Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) bhi us se mohabbat kartey hain. phir wo aasman mein awaz detey hain ke Allah falan se mohabbat karta hai tum bhi us se mohabbat karo chunanche aasman waaley bhi us se mohabbat karne lagtey hain aur is tarah poori zameen mein bhi usey maqbooliyat hasil ho jati hai.''
7486,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhaarey paas raat aur din ke Farishtey ek ke baad ek aatey hain aur Asr aur fajr ki Namaz mein 2 waqt ke Farishtey ikatthey hotey hain. phir jab wo Farishtey uper jatey hain jinhoney raat tumharey sath guzari hai to Allah Taala unse poochhta hai halanke wo bandon ke haal ka sabse zyada jaanney wala hai ke tum ne mere bandon ko kis haal mein chhodaa? wo jawab detey hain ke ham ne unhein is haal mein chhoda ke wo Namaz padh rahe they aur jab ham unke paas gaey jab bhi wo Namaz padh rahe they.''
7487,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere paas Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aaey aur mujhey bashaarat di ke jo shakhs us haal mein mareyga ke wo Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik nahi thahraataa hoga to wo jannat mein jaeyga maine puchha bhaley hi usne chori aur zina bhi kya ho? farmaya ke bhaley hi us ne chori aur zina kya ho.''
7488,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey fulaan! jab tum apne bistar par jao to ye dua karo (اللهم أسلمت نفسي إليك، Mina ووجهت وجهي إليك وفوضت أمري إليك، Mina وألجأت ظهري إليك، Mina رغبة ورهبة إليك، Mina لا ملجأ wla منجا منك إلا إليك، Mina آمنت بكتابك الذي أنزلت، Mina وبنبيك الذي أرسلت) ''aey Allaah! maine apni jaan terey sipurd kar di aur apna rukh teri taraf mod diya aur apna mamla terey sipurd kar diya aur teri panah li, teri taraf raghbat ki wjah se aur tujh se dar kar. terey siwa koi panah aur nijat ki jagah nahi, main teri kitab par eman laya jo to ne nazil ki aur terey Nabi par eman laya jo to ne bhejey."" pas agar tum aaj raat mar gaey to fitrat par marogey aur subah ko zinda uthey to sawab milega."
7489,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Khandaq ki jang ke din farmaya ''aey Allah ! kitab Quran ke nazil karne waale, jald hisab leney waale, un dushman jamaton ko shikast de aur unke paon dagmagaa de. ''Humaidii ne usey yun riwayat kya ke ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ismail bin abi Khalid ne bayan kya aur unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
7490,"ye us waqt nazil hui jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein chhup kar ibadat kya kartey they. jab aap Namaz mein awaz buland kartey to mushrekeen suntey aur Quran Majeed aur uske nazil karne waley Allah ko aur uske laney waley Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko gali detey (aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi) usi liye Allah Taala ne farmaya ( wla تجهر بصلاتك wla تخافت بها‏ (ke '' apni Namaz mein na awaz buland karo aur na bilkul aahista yani awaz itni buland bhi na karke mushrekeen sun lein aur itni aahista bhi na karke aap ke sathi bhi na sun sakein balke unke darmyan ka rasta ikhtiyar kar.'' matlab ye hai ke itni awaz se padh ke terey ashaab sun lein aur Quran seekh lein, us se zyada chilla kar na padh."
7491,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke ibne-Aadam mujhey takleef pahunchata hai, zamane ko bura bhala kehta hai, halanke main hi zamane ka paida karne wala hun, mere hi hath mein tamam kaam hain, main jis tarah chahta ho raat aur din ko phertaa rehta hoon.''"
7492,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Shaan wala Allah farmata hai ke roza khalis mere liye hota hai aur main hi iska badla deta hun. banda apni shahwat, khaanaa-peenaa meri raza ke liye chhorta hai aur roza gunahon se bachney ki dhaal hai aur roze-daar ke liye do khushiyaan hain. aik khushi us waqt jab wo iftaar karta hai aur aik khushi us waqt jab wo apne rab se milta hai aur roze-daar ke munh ki boo, Allah ke nazdeek mushk anbar ki khushbu se zyada pakeeza hai.''"
7493,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ayyoob (Alaihissalam) kapdey utaar kar naha rahe they ke soney ki tiiddiiyoun ka aik dal un par aa kar gira aur aap unhein kapdey mein sametney lagey. unke rab ne unhein pukara ke aey Ayyoob! kya maine tujhey maaldaar bana kar in tiiddiiyoun se be-parwaa nahi kar diya hai. unhon-ne arz kya ke kyon nahi beshak tu ney mujh ko be-parwaa maaldaar kya hai magar terey Fazal aur karam aur rehmat se bhi main kahin be-parwaa ho sakta hoon.''
7494,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''hamaaraa rab tabarak w taala har raat aasmaani duniya par aata hai. us waqt jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey baqi reh jata hai aur kehta hai ke mujhey kon bulata hai ke main usey jawab dun. mujh se kon mangta hai ke main usey ataa' karun. mujh se kon maghfirat talab karta hai main uski maghfirat karoon?''
7495,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maano duniya mein ham sabse aakhiri ummat hain lekin aakhirat mein sabse aagey hongey.''
7496,Allah Taala farmata hai ke tum kharch karo to main tum par kharch karunga .
7497,(Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah !) ye Khadija (Raziallahu anha) jo aap ke paas bartan mein khana ya pani lekar aati hain unhein unke rab ki taraf se salam kahey aur unhein khauldaar moutii ke aik mahal ki jannat mein khushkhabri sunaaiye jis mein na shor hoga aur na koi takleef hogi.
7498,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke jannat mein, maine apne nek bandon ke liye wo cheezein taiyaar kar rakhi hain jinhein na aankhon ne dekha, na kanon ne suna aur na kisi insan ke dil mein unka khayal guzraa.''"
7499,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab raat mein tahajjud padhney uthtey to kehtey (اللهم لك الحمد أنت نور السموات والأرض، Mina ولك الحمد أنت قيم السموات والأرض، Mina ولك الحمد أنت رب السموات والأرض، Mina ومن فيهن أنت الحق، Mina ووعدك الحق وقولك الحق، Mina ولقاؤك الحق، Mina والجنة حق، Mina والنار حق، Mina والنبيون حق، Mina والساعة حق، Mina اللهم لك أسلمت، Mina وبك آمنت، Mina وعليك توكلت، Mina وإليك أنبت، Mina وبك خاصمت، Mina وإليك حاكمت، Mina فاغفر لي ما قدمت وما أخرت، Mina وما أسررت وما أعلنت، Mina أنت إلهي، Mina لا إله إلا أنت) ''hamd terey hi liye hai ke to aasman aur zameen ka noor hai. hamd terey hi liye hai ke to aasman aur zameen ka thamney wala hai. hamd terey hi liye hai ke to aasman aur zameen ka aur jo kuchh usmein hai sab ka rab hai. to sach hai, tera wada sachcha hai aur tera qaul sachcha hai, teri mulaqat sachchii hai, jannat sach hai aur dozakh sach hai. sarey anbiya sachey hain aur qiyamat sach hai. aey Allah ! main terey samney hi jhukaa, tujh par eman laya. tujh par bharosa kya, teri hi taraf rujoo kya, terey hi samney apna jhagdaa pesh karta aur tujh hi se apna faisla chahta hun. isliye to meri maghfirat kar de agley pichhley tamam gunahon ki jo maine chipa kar kiye aur jo zahir kiye. to hi mera maabood hai, terey siwa aur koi maabood nahi.''"
7500,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke barey mein jab tohmat lagaaney walon ne un par tohmat lagai thi aur Allah ne us se unhein barii qarar diya tha. un sab ne bayan kya aur har aik ne mujh se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki bayan ki hui baat ka aik hissey bayan kya. Ummul-Momenin ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey ye khayal nahi tha ke Allah Taala meri paakii bayan karne ke liye wahi nazil karega jiski tilawat hogi. mere dil mein mera darja us se bahut kam tha ke Allah mere barey mein (Qur'aan Majeed mein) wahi nazil karega jiski tilawat hogi. albatta mujhey ummeed thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) koi khuwab dekhengey jiske zariey Allah meri Bar'at (Tauba) kar dega. lekin Allah Taala ne ye aayatein (إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك‏) nazil ki hain, das aayaate."
7501,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ka irshad giraamii hai : ''aey farishton ! jab mera banda kisi burai ka irada karey to jab tak wo is par amal karey to phir uske barabar gunah likho aur agar wo uske mutabiq amal karey to phir uske barabar gunah likho. agar wo mere khof se us burai ko tark kar de to uske liye aik neki likho. aur agar koi banda neki karna chahey to uske liye iraadey hi par aik neki likh do aur agar is par amal kar ley to das guna se saat (7) sou guna tak neki likho.''
7502,"ham se Ismaaeel-bin-abdullaah ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha mujh se Sulaimaan-bin-Bilaal ne bayan kya, unse Muaawiya-bin-abii-muzarrid  ne bayan kya aur unse Saeed-bin-yasaar ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne makhlooq paida ki aur jab us se farigh ho gaya to riiham khada huaa, Allah ne farmaya ke thahar jaa. usne kaha ke ye qata' rahami (nataa todnaa) se teri panah maangney ka maqam hai. Allah Taala ne farmaya kya tum is par razi nahi ke main nataa ko jodney waley se apne raham ka nataa jodoon aur nataa ko kaatney walon se juda ho jaun. usne kaha ke zaroor, mere rab! Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir yahi tera maqam hai. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne (sura Muhammad ki) ye aayat padhi ( فهل عسيتم إن توليتم أن تفسدوا في الأرض وتقطعوا أرحامكم‏ )'' mumkin hai ke agar tum Hakim bin jao to zameen mein fasaad karo aur qata' rahami karo.''"
7503,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein barish hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala farmata hai mere kuchh bandey subah, kaafir ho kar kartey hain aur kuchh bandey subah, momin ho kar kartey hain."
7504,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke jab mera banda mujh se mulaqat pasand karta hai to main bhi us se mulaqat pasand karta hun aur jab wo mujh se mulaqat na-pasand karta hai to main bhi na-pasand karta hoon.''
7505,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke main apne bandey ke guman ke sath hun jo wo mere mutaalliq rakhta hai.''
7506,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik shakhs ne jisne (banii-Israaeel mein se) koi nek kaam kabhi nahi kya tha. wasiiyat ki ke jab wo mar jaey to usey jalaa daalein aur uski aadhi raakh khushkii mein aur aadhi dariya mein bikher dein kyonke Allah ki qism agar Allah ne mujh par qaabu pa liya to aisa azab mujh ko dega jo duniya ke kisi shakhs ko bhi wo nahi dega. phir Allah ne samandar ko hukm diya aur us ne tamam raakh jama kar di jo iske andar thi. phir us ne khushkii ko hukm diya aur us ne bhi apni tamam raakh jama kar di jo iske andar thi. phir Allah Taala ne us se puchha tu ney aisa kyon kya tha? us ne arz kya aey rab! terey khof se maine aisa kya aur to sabse zyada jaanney wala hai. isliye Allah Taala ne usko bakhsh diyaa.''
7507,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik bandey ne bahut gunah kiye aur kaha : aey mere rab ! main tera hi gunahgaar banda hun to mujhey bakhsh de. Allah rabbul-izzat ne farmaya : mera banda janta hai ke uska koi rab zaroor hai jo gunah maaf karta hai aur gunah ki wjah se saza bhi deta hai maine apne bandey ko bakhsh diya phir banda ruka raha jitna Allah ne chaha aur phir us ne gunah kya aur arz kya : aey mere rab ! maine dobara gunah kar liya, usey bhi bakhsh de. Allah Taala ne farmaya : mera banda janta hai ke uska rab zaroor hai jo gunah maaf karta hai aur uske badley mein saza bhi deta hai, maine apne bandey ko bakhsh diya. phir jab tak Allah ne chaha banda gunah se ruka raha aur phir us ne gunah kya aur Allah ke huzoor mein arz kya : aey mere rab! maine gunah phir kar liya hai to mujhey bakhsh de. Allah Taala ne farmaya mera banda janta hai ke uska aik rab zaroor hai jo gunah maaf karta warna uski wjah se saza bhi deta hai maine apne bandey ko bakhsh diya. teen martaba , isliye ab jo chahey amal kare."
7508,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pichhli ummaton mein se aik shakhs ka zikr kya. iske mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kalima farmaya yani Allah ne usey maal aur aulad sab kuchh diya tha. jab iske marney ka waqt qareeb aaya to usne apne ladkon se puchha ke main tumharey liye kaisa bap Sabit hua. unhon-ne kaha ke behtreen baap, is par usne kaha ke lekin tumharey bap ne Allah ke yahan koi neki nahi bheji hai aur agar kahin Allah ne mujhey pakad liya to sakht azab karega to dekho jab main mar jaun to mujhey jalaa dena. yahan tak ke jab main koila ho jaun to usey khub pees lena aur jis din tez aandhii aaey usmein meri ye raakh uda dena. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par us ne apne beton se pukhta wada liya aur Allah ki qism ke uske ladkon ne aisa hi kya. jalaa kar raakh kar daalaa, phir unhon-ne uski raakh ko tez hawa ke din uda diya. phir Allah Taala ne (كن‏) ka lafz farmaya ke ho ja to wo fauran aik mard bin gaya jo khada hua tha. Allah Taala ne farmaya, aey mere bandey ! tujhey kis baat ne is par aamada kya ke tu ney ye kaam karaya. usne kaha ke terey khof ne. bayan kya ke Allah Taala ne usko koi saza nahi di balke is par raham kya. phir maine ye baat abu-Usman-nahdii se bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha ke maine usey Sulaimaan-faarsii se suna, albatta unhon-ne ye lafz zyada kiye ke (أذروني في البحر‏) yani meri raakh ko dariya mein daal dena ya kuchh aisa hi bayan kya. ham se Moosaa-bin-Ismaaeel ne bayan kya, kaha ham se moa'tamir-bin-Sulaimaan ne bayan kya aur us ne (لم يبتئر‏) ke alfaz kahey aur khaleefa-bin-khayaat (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke shekh) ne kaha ham se Motamir ne bayan kya phir yahi hadis naql ki. usmein (لم يبتئر‏) hai. Qatada ne iske mana ye kiye hain yani koi neki aakhirat ke liye zakheera nahi ki."
7509,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ke din meri shafaat qabool ki jaeygi. main kahunga : aey rab! jiske dil mein raai ke daane ke barabar bhi eman ho usko bhi jannat mein dakhil farma de. aisey log jannat mein dakhil kar diye jaengey. main phir arz karunga : aey rab! jannat mein usey bhi dakhil kar de jiske dil mein maamooli sa bhi eman ho. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maano main us waqt bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ki taraf dekh raha hun."
7510,"Basra ke kuchh log hamarey paas jama ho gaey. phir ham Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey aur apne sath Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi le gaey taake wo hamarey liye shafaat ki hadis poochhein. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) apne mahal mein they aur jab ham pahunchey to wo chasht ki Namaz padh rahe they. ham ne mulaqat ki ijazat chahi aur hamein ijazat mil gaee. us waqt wo apne bistar par baithey they. ham ne Sabit se kaha tha ke hadis shafaat se pahley unse aur kuchh na poochhna . chunanche unhon-ne kaha : aey abu-Hamza ! ye aap ke bhai Basra se aaey hain aur aap se shafaat ki hadis poochhna chahtey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ka din jab aayega to log thaathein maartey huey samandar ki tarah zahir hongey. phir wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur unse kahengey ke hamari apne rab ke paas shafaat keejiye. wo kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi hun tum Ibrahim ke paas jao, wo Allah ke khaleel hain. log Ibrahim ke paas aaeingey wo bhi kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi hun, haan tum Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao ke wo Allah se sharf ham-kalaamii paaney waley hain. log Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur wo bhi kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi hun, albatta tum Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao ke wo Allah ki Rooh aur uska kalima hain. chunanche log Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey wo bhi kahengey ke main is qaabil nahi hun, haan tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao. log mere paas aaeingey aur main kahunga ke main shafaat ke liye hun aur phir main apne rab se ijazat chaahoonga aur mujhey ijazat di jaeygi aur Allah Taala ta'reefon ke alfaz mujhey ilhaam karega jinke zariey mein Allah ki hamd bayan karunga jo is waqt mujhey yad nahi hain. chunanche jab main ye ta'reefein bayan karunga Allah ke huzoor mein sajda karne wala ho jaaunga to mujh se kaha jaeyga : aey Muhammad ! apna sar uthao , jo kaho wo suna jaeyga, jo maangogey wo diya jaeyga, jo shafaat karogey qabool ki jaeygi. phir main kahunga : aey rab! meri ummat , meri ummat , kaha jaeyga ke jao aur un logon ko dozakh se nikal lo jinke dil mein zarra ya raai barabar bhi eman ho. chunanche main jaaunga aur aisa hi karunga . phir main lautoonga aur yahi ta'reefein phir karunga aur Allah ke liye sajde mein chala jaaunga mujh se kaha jaeyga apna sar uthao kaho, aap ki suni jaeygi, main kahunga : aey rab! meri ummat, meri ummat. Allah Taala farmaeyga : jao aur jiske dil mein aik raai ke daane ke kam se kam tar hisse ke barabar bhi eman ho usey bhi jahannam se nikaal lo. phir main jaaunga aur nikaalunga. phir jab ham Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se nikley to maine apne kuchh sathiyon se kaha ke hamein imam Hasan Basri ke paas bhi chalnaa chaahiye, wo us waqt Abu-Khaleefa ke makan mein they aur unse wo hadis bayan karna chahiye jo Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ham se bayan ki hai. chunanche ham unke paas aaey aur unhein salam kya. phir unhon-ne hamein ijazat di aur ham ne unse kaha : aey abu-Saeed! ham aap ke paas aap ke bhai Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan se aaey hain aur unhon-ne ham se jo shafaat ke mutaalliq hadis bayan ki, us jaisi hadis ham ne nahi suni, unhon-ne kaha ke bayan karo. ham ne unse hadis bayan ki jab us maqam tak pahunchey to unhon-ne kaha ke aur bayan karo, ham ne kaha ke us se zyada unhon-ne nahi bayan ki. unhon-ne kaha ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) jab sihatmand they, bees saal ab se pahley to unhon-ne mujh se ye hadis bayan ki thi. mujhey malum nahi ke wo baqi bhool gaey ya isliye bayan karna na-pasand kya ke kahin log bharosa na kar baithein. ham ne kaha abu-Saeed! phir ham se wo hadis bayan keejiye. aap is par hansey aur farmaya : insan bada jald baaz paida kya gaya hai. maine iska zikr hi isliye kya hai ke tum se bayan karna chahta hun. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se isi tarah hadis bayan ki jis tarah tum se bayan ki (aur is mein ye lafz aur badhaatey ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir main chothi martaba lautoonga aur wahi ta'reefein karunga aur Allah ke liye sajde mein chala jaaunga. Allah farmaeyga : aey Muhammad! apna sar uthaao, jo kahogey suna jaeyga jo maango ke diya jaeyga jo shafaat karogey qabool ki jaeygi. mein kahunga : aey rab! mujhey unke barey mein bhi ijazat dijiye jinhoney la ilaaha-illallaah kaha hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga meri izzat, mere jalaal, meri kibriyaaii, meri badaai ki qism ! usmein se ( mein) unhein bhi nikalunga jinhoney kalima la ilaaha-illallaah kaha hai."
7511,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein sabse baad mein dakhil honey wala aur dozakh se sabse baad mein nikalney wala wo shakhs hoga jo ghisat kar niklega, us se iska rab kahega jannat mein dakhil ho jaa, wo kahega mere rab! jannat to bilkul bhari hui hai, phir Allah Taala farmaeyga terey liye duniya ke das guna hai.''"
7512,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se har shakhs se tumhara rab is tarah baat karega ke tumharey aur uske darmyan koi tarjuman nahi hoga wo apne daain taraf dekhega aur usey apne aamaal ke siwa aur kuchh nazar nahi aayega aur wo apni baain taraf dekhega aur usey apne aamaal ke siwa kuchh nazar nahi aayega. phir apne samney dekhega to apne samney jahannam ke siwa aur koi cheez na dekhega. to jahannam se bacho chahe khajoor ke aik tukdey hi ke zariey ho sakey.'' Aamash ne bayan kya ke mujh se Amr-bin-Murra ne bayan kya, unse khaisma ne isi tarah aur is mein ye lafz zyada kiye ke (jahannam se bacho) chahe aik achi baat hi ke zariey ho."
7513,"ham se Usman bin abi Sheba ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se Jarir ne bayan kya, unse Mansoor ne bayan kya, unse Ibrahim ne bayan kya, unse Ubeda ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke"
7514,aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : sargoshi ke barey mein aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kis tarah suna hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke tum mein se koi apne rab ke qareeb jaeyga yahan tak ke Allah Taala apna parda is par daal dega aur kahega tu ney ye ye amal kya tha? banda kahega ke haan. chunanche wo iska iqrar karega . phir Allah Taala farmaeyga ke maine duniya mein terey gunah par parda daala tha aur aaj bhi tujhey maaf karta hun.
7515,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Adam (Alaihissalam) aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ne bahas ki, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke aap Adam hain jinhoney apni nasl ko jannat se nikaalaa. Adam (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke aap Musa hain jinhein Allah ne apne paigham aur kalam ke liye muntakhab kya aur phir bhi aap mujhey aik aisi baat ke liye malaamat kartey hain jo Allah ne meri paidaaish se pahley hi meri taqdeer mein likh di thi, chunanche Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aaey."
7516,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''emaan waley qiyamat ke din jama kiye jaeinge aur wo kahengey ke kash! koi hamari shafaat karta taake ham apni us haalat se nijat paatey, chunanche wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaeingey aur kahengey ke aap Adam hain insanon ke pardaadaa. Allah ne aapko apne hath se paida kya, aapko sajda karne ka farishton ko hukm diya aur har cheez ke naam aapko sikhaaey to aap apne rab ke huzoor mein hamari shafaat karein, aap jawab dengey ke main is qaabil nahi hun aur aap apni ghalati unhein yad dilaaeingey jo aap se hui thi. ''"
7517,"unhon-ne wo waqia bayan kya jis raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko masjid Kaba se meraaj ke liye ley jaya gaya ke wahi aaney se pahley aap ke paas Farishtey aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjide-Haraam mein soey huey they. unmein se aik ne puchha ke wo kon hain? doosrey ne jawab diya ke wo unmein sabse behtar hain teesrey ne kaha ke unmein jo sabse behtar hain unhein ley lo. us raat ko bas itna hi waqia pesh aaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad unhein nahi dekha. yahan tak ke wo dusri raat aaey jabke aap ka dil dekh raha tha aur aap ki aankhen so rahi thin. lekin dil nahi so raha tha. anbiya ka yahi haal hota hai. unki aankhen soti hain lekin unke dil nahi sotey . chunanche unhon-ne aap se baat nahi ki. balke aapko utha kar zamzam ke kuwein ke paas laey. yahan Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aap ka kaam sanbhaalaa aur aap ke galey se dil ke nichey tak Sina chaak kya aur seeney aur pet ko paak karke zamzam ke pani se usey apne hath se dhoya yahan tak ke aap ka pet saaf ho gaya. phir aap ke paas soney ka tasht laya gaya jis mein soney ka aik bartan eman w hikmat se bharaa hua tha. us se aap ke seeney aur halaq ki ragon ko siyaa aur usey barabar kar diya. phir aapko lekar aasman duniya par chadhey aur uske darwazon mein se aik darwazey par dastak di. aasman walon ne unse puchha aap kon hain? unhon-ne kaha ke Jibraeel unhon-ne puchha aur aap ke sath kon hai? jawab diya ke mere sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain. puchha : kya unhein bulaya gaya hai? jawab diya ke haan. aasman walon ne kaha khub achchhey aaey aur apne hi logon mein aaey ho. aasman waley us se khush huey. unmein se kisi ko malum nahi hota ke Allah Taala zameen mein kya karna chahta hai jab tak wo unhein bata na de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aasmaane-duniyaa par Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paya. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aap se kaha ke ye aap ke buzurg tareen dada Adam hain aap unhein salam kijiye . Adam (Alaihissalam) ne salam ka jawab diya. kaha ke khub achchhey aaey aur apne hi logon mein aaey ho. Mubarak ho apne betey ko , aap kya hi achchhey betey hain. aap ne aasman duniya mein 2 nehrein dekhiin jo bah rahi thin. puchha aey Jibraeel ! ye nehrein kaisi hain? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne jawab diya ke ye neel aur Furaat ka manba' (saurce) hai. phir aap aasman par aur chaley to dekha ke aik dusri nehar hai jiske uper motii aur zabarjad ka mahal hai. is par apna hath maara to wo mashk hai. puchha : Jibraeel ! ye kya hai? jawab diya ke ye kausar hai jisey Allah ne aap ke liye mehfooz rakha hai. phir aap doosrey aasman par chadhey . farishton ne yahan bhi wahi sawal kya jo pahley aasman par kya tha. kon hain? kaha : Jibraeel . puchha aap ke sath kon hain? kaha Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) . puchha kya unhein bulaya gaya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. Farishtey boley unhein marhaba aur bashaarat ho. phir aapko lekar teesrey aasman par chadhey aur yahan bhi wahi sawal kya jo pahley aur doosrey aasman par kya tha. phir chauthey aasman par lekar chadhey aur yahan bhi wahi sawal kya. phir paanchwein aasman par aapko lekar chadhey aur yahan bhi wahi sawal kya phir chhatey aasman par aapko lekar chadhey aur yahan bhi wahi sawal kya. phir aapko lekar saatwen aasman par chadhey aur yahan bhi wahi sawal kya. har aasman par anbiya hain jinke naam aap ne liye. mujhey ye yad hai ke Idrees (Alaihissalam) doosrey aasman par, Harun (Alaihissalam) chauthey aasman par, aur doosrey Nabi paanchwein aasman par. jinke naam mujhey yad nahi aur Ibrahim chhatey aasman par aur Musa (Alaihissalam) saatwen aasman par. ye unhein Allah Taala ne sharfe-ham kalaamii ki wjah se fazeelat mili thi. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : mere rab! mera khayal nahi tha ke kisi ko mujh se badhaya jaeyga phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) unhein lekar us se bhi uper gaey jiska ilm Allah ke siwa aur kisi ko nahi yahan tak ke aapko sidratul-muntahaa par lekar aaey aur rabbul-izzat Allah tabarak w taala se qareeb huey aur itney qareeb jaisey kamaan ke donon kinarey ya us se bhi qareeb . phir Allah ne aur dusri baton ke sath aap ki ummat par din aur raat mein pachaas namazon ki wahi ki. phir aap utrey aur jab Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas pahunchey to unhon-ne aapko rok liya aur puchha : aey Muhammad ! aap ke rab ne aap se kya ahad liya hai? farmaya ke mere rab ne mujh se din aur raat mein pachaas namazon ka ahad liya hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke aap ki ummat mein uski taqat nahi. wapas jaaiye aur apni aur apni ummat ki taraf se kami ki darkhaast keejiye. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unhon-ne bhi ishara kya ke yahan agar chaahein to behtar hai. chunanche aap phir unhein lekar Allah Taala ki bargah mein hazir huey aur apne maqam par khadey ho kar arz kya : aey rab! ham se kami kar de kyonke meri ummat iski taqat nahi rakhtii. chunanche Allah Taala ne das namazon ki kami kar di. phir aap Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaey to unhon-ne aapko rokaa. Musa (Alaihissalam) aapko isi tarah barabar Allah rabbul-izzat ke paas wapas kartey rahe. yahan tak ke panch namazein ho gaiin. panch namazon par bhi unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko rokaa aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! maine apni qaum Bani-Israeel ka tajriba is se kam par kya hai wo kamzor Sabit huey aur unhon-ne chhod diya. aap ki ummat to jism , dil , badan , nazar aur kaan har eitibaar se kamzor hai, aap wapas jaaiye aur Allah rabbul-izzat usmein bhi kami kar dega. har martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ki taraf mutwajjeh hotey they taake unse mashwara lein aur Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) usey na-pasand nahi kartey they. jab wo aapko paanchwein martaba bhi le gaey to arz kya : aey mere rab! meri ummat jism, dil, nigaah aur band har haisiyat se kamzor hai, to ham se aur kami kar de. Allah Taala ne is par farmaya ke wo qaul mere yahan badla nahi jata jaisa ke maine tum par ummul-kitaab mein farz kya hai. aur farmaya ke har neki ka sawab das guna hai to ye ummul-kitaab mein pachaas namazein hain lekin tum par farz panch hi hain. chunanche aap Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas wapas aaey aur unhon-ne puchha : kya hua? aap ne kaha ke ham se ye kami ki ke har neki ke badley das ka sawab milega. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke maine Bani-Israeel ko us se kam par aazmaya hai aur unhon-ne chhod diya. to aap wapas jaaiye aur mazeed kami karaaiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par kaha : aey Moosaa, Allah ki qism ! mujhey apne rab se ab sharm aati hai kyonke baar-baar aa ja chuka hun. unhon-ne kaha ke phir Allah ka naam lekar utar jao. phir jab aap bedaar huey to masjide-Haraam mein they. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjide-Haraam hi mein they ke jaag uthey, jaag uthney se ye murad hai ke wo haalat meraaj ki jati rahi aur aap apni haalat mein aa gaey."
7518,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala jannat walon se kahega : aey jannat waalo! wo bolengey hazir teri khidmat ke liye muste'ad, saari bhalai terey donon hathon mein hai. Allah Taala poochhega : kya tum khush ho? wo jawab dengey kyon nahi ham khush hongey, aey rab! aur tu ney hamein wo cheezein ata ki hain jo kisi makhlooq ko nahi ata kin. Allah Taala farmaeyga kya main tumhen us se afzal inaam na dun? jannati poochhengey : aey rab! us se afzal kya cheez ho sakti hai Allah Taala farmaeyga ke main apni khushi tum par utaartaa hun aur ab kabhi tum se naraz nahi hoonga.''"
7519,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din guftgu kar rahe they, us waqt aap ke paas aik badwi bhi tha ( farmaya (ke ahle-jannat mein se aik shakhs ne Allah Taala se kheti ki ijazat chahi to Allah Taala ne farmaya ke kya wo sab kuchh tumharey paas nahi hai jo tum chahtey ho? wo kahega ke zaroor lekin main chahta hun ke kheti karun. chunanche bahut jaldi wo beej daalega aur palak jhapakney tak iska ugnaa , barabar katnaa aur pahadon ki tarah ghalley ke anbaar lag jana ho jaeyga Allah Taala kahega : ibne-Aadam! usey ley-ley, terey pet ko koi cheez nahi bhar saktii. dehati ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! iska maza to qureshi ya Ansari hi uthaaeingey kyonke wahi kheti baadii waley hain, ham to kisaan hain nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat sun kar hansi aa gaee."
7520,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kon sa gunah Allah ke yahan sabse bada hai? farmaya ye ke tum Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thehrao halanke usi ne tumhen paida kya hai. maine kaha ye to bahut bada gunah hai. maine arz kya : phir kon sa ? farmaya ye ke tum apne bachchey ko us khatre ki wjah se qatl kar do ke wo tumharey sath khaaeyga. maine arz kya ke phir kaun? farmaya ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo.
7521,"khaana Kaba ke paas 2 Saqafi aur aik qureshi ya (ye kaha ke) 2 qureshi aur aik Saqafi jama huey jinke pet ki charbi bahut thi ( taund badi thi) aur jin mein soojh bojh ki badi kami thi. unmein se aik ne kaha ke tumhara khayal hai ke Allah wo sab kuchh sunta hai jo ham kehtey hain. doosrey ne kaha ke jab ham zor se boltey hain to sunta hai lekin agar ham aahista boliin to nahi sunta . is par Allah ne ye aayat nazil ki) وما كنتم تستترون أن يشهد عليكم سمعكم wla أبصاركم wla جلودكم‏ ( ''tum jo duniya mein chhup kar gunah kartey they, to is dar se nahi ke terey kaan tumhari aankhen aur tumharey chamdey tumharey khilaf qiyamat ke din gawahi dengey'' aakhir tak."
7522,"tum ahle-kitab se unki kitaabon ke masayel ke barey mein kyonkar sawal kartey ho, tumharey paas khud Allah ki kitab maujood hai jo zamane ke eitibaar se bhi tum se sabse zyada qareeb hai, tum usey padhtey ho, wo khalis hai is mein koi milawat nahi."
7523,"aey musalmaanon! tum ahle-kitab se kisi mas'ale mein kyon poochhtey ho. tumhari kitab jo Allah Taala ne tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par nazil ki hai wo Allah ke yahan se bilkul taaza aai hai, khalis hai is mein koi milawat nahi hui aur Allah Taala ne khud tumhen bata diya hai ke ahle-kitab ne Allah ki kitaabon ko badal dala. wo hath se aik kitab likhtey aur dawa kartey ke ye Allah ki taraf se hai taake iske zariey se thodi poonjii hasil karein, tum ko jo Allah ne Quran w hadis ka ilm diya hai kya wo tum ko us se mana nahi karta ke tum Deen ki baatein ahle-kitab se poochho. Allah ki qism ! ham to unke kisi aadmi ko nahi dekhtey ke jo kuchh tumharey uper nazil hua hai iske mutaalliq wo tum se poochhtey hon."
7524,"( sura qiyaama mein) Allah Taala ka irshaad (لا تحرك به لسانك) ke mutaalliq ke wahi nazil hoti hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par iska bahut baar padta hai aur aap apne hont hilatey mujh se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main tumhen hilaa ke dikhaataa hon jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hilatey they. Saeed ne kaha ke jis tarah Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) hont hilaa kar dikhaaey they, main tumharey samney isi tarah hilata hun. chunanche unhon-ne apne hont hilaaey . (ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (لا تحرك به لسانك لتعجل به * إن علينا جمعه وقرآنه)  yaanii '' tumharey seeney mein Quran ka jama dena aur usko padha dena hamara kaam hai jab ham ( Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ki zaban par) usko padh chukein us waqt tum iske padhney ki pairwi karo.'' matlab ye hai ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ke padhtey waqt kaan laga kar suntey raho aur khamosh raho, ye hamara zimma hai ke ham tum se waisaa hi padhwaa dengey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke is aayat ke utarney ke baad jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aatey ( Quran sunatey ( to aap kaan laga kar suntey . jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) chaley jatey to aap logon ko isi tarah padh kar suna detey jaisey Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aapko padh kar sunaya tha."
7525,"Allah Taala ke irshad ( wla تجهر بصلاتك wla تخافت بها‏ (ke barey mein ke ye aayat jab nazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein chhup kar) aa'maale-Islaam ada kartey they) lekin jab apne sahaba ko Namaz padhatey to Quran Majeed buland awaz se padhtey , jab mushrekeen suntey to Quran Majeed ko , iske utaarney waley ko aur usey lekar aaney waley ko gali detey. chunanche Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke apni qirat mein awaz buland na karein ke mushrekeen sunein aur phir Quran ko gali dein aur na itna aahista hi padhein ke aap ke sahaba bhi na sun sakein balke unke darmyan ka rasta ikhtiyar karein."
7526,"aayat ( wla تجهر بصلاتك wla تخافت بها‏ ( dua ke barey mein nazil hui, yani dua na bahut chilla kar maang na aahista balke darmyaana rasta ikhtiyar kar."
7527,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo khush aawaazi se Quran nahi padhta wo ham musalmanon ke tareeq par nahi hai.'' aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa doosrey logon ne us hadis mein itna zyada kya hai yani usko pukar kar na padhey .
7528,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' rashk sirf 2 aadmiyon par kya ja sakta hai, aik is par jisey Allah ne Quran ka ilm diya aur wo uski tilawat raat din karta hai to aik dekhney wala kehta hai ke kash! mujhey bhi usi jaisa Quran ka ilm hota to main bhi uski tarah tilawat karta rehta aur doosra wo shakhs hai jisey Allah ne maal diya aur wo usey uske haq mein kharch karta hai jisey dekhney wala kehta hai ke kash! mujhey bhi Allah itna maal deta to main bhi isi tarah kharch karta jaisey ye karta hai.''"
7529,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' rashk ke qaabil to 2 hi aadmi hain. aik wo jisey Allah ne Quran diya aur wo uski tilawat raat din karta rehta hai aur doosra wo jisey Allah ne maal diya ho aur wo usey raat w din kharch karta raha. '' Ali-bin-Abdullaah ne kaha ke maine ye hadis Sufiyan-bin-Uena se kai baar suni ( أخبرنا (ke lafzon ke sath unhein kehta suna bawajud iske unki ye hadis sahi aur muttasil hai.
7530,hamarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein apne rab ke paighaamaat mein se ye paigham pahunchaya ke ham mein se jo (fee sabeelillaah ( qatl kya jaeyga wo jannat mein jaeyga
7531,"agar koi tum se ye bayan karta hai ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi cheez chhipaaii, (aur dusri sanad) aur Muhammad-bin Yusuf fariyaabii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Aamir aqadii ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shoba bin Hajjaj ne, unse Ismail bin abi Khalid ne, unse Shabi ne, unse Masruq ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke agar tum se koi ye bayan karta hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahi mein kuchh chipa liya to uski tasdeeq na karna (wo jhoota hai) kyonke Allah Taala khud farmata hai ( ya أيها الرسول بلغ ما أنزل إليك من ربك وإن لم تفعل فما بلغت رسالته‏ (ke ''aey rasool! pahuncha dijiye wo paigham jo aap ke paas aap ke rab ki taraf se nazil hua hai aur agar aap ne ye nahi kya to aap apne rab ka paigham nahi pahunchaayaa.''"
7532,aik sahib ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kon sa gunah Allah ke nazdeek sabse bada hai? farmaya ke tum Allah ki ibadat mein kisi ko bhi saajhii banao halanke tumhen Allah ne paida kya hai. puchha phir kon sa ? farmaya ye ke tum apne bachchey ko is khof se mar dalo ke wo tumharey sath khaaeyga. puchha phir kon sa? farmaya ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo. chunanche Allah Taala ne (sura furqan mein) uski tasdeeq mein Quran nazil farmaayaa (والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر wla يقتلون النفس التي حرم الله إلا بالحق wla يزنون ومن يفعل ذلك) ''aur wo log jo Allah ke sath kisi doosrey ma'boode-baatil ko nahi pukaartey aur jo kisi aisey ki jaan nahi letey jisey Allah ne haram kya hai siwa haq ke aur jo zina nahi kartey aur jo koi aisa karega wo gunah se bhid jaaeyga.''
7533,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' pichhli ummaton ke muqable main tumhara wujood aisa hai jaisey Asr aur maghrib ke darmyan ka waqt, Taurait walon ko Taurait di gaee to unhon-ne is par amal kya yahan tak ke din aadha ho gaya aur wo aajiz ho gaey. phir unhein eik-eik qirat diya gaya. phir ahal Injeel ko Injeel di gaee aur unhon-ne is par amal kya yahan tak ke Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, unhein bhi eik-eik qirat diya gaya. phir tumhen Quran diya gaya aur tum ne is par amal kya yahan tak ke maghrib ka waqt ho gaya, tumhen 2-2 qirat diye gaey, is par ahle-kitaab ne kaha ke ye ham se amal mein kam hain aur ajr mein zyada . Allah Taala ne farmaya kya maine tumhara haq dene mein koi zulm kya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya ke nahi. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir ye mera Fazal hai main jisey chaahoon dun."
7534,"aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kon sa amal sabse afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya ke apne waqt par Namaz padhna aur waalidain ke sath nek mamla karnaa, phir Allah ke rastey mein jihad karna."
7535,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas maal aaya aur aap ne usmein se kuchh logon ko diya aur kuchh ko nahi diya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke is par kuchh log naraz huey hain to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik shakhs ko deta hun aur doosrey ko nahi deta aur jisey nahi deta wo mujhey us se zyada azeez hota hai jisey deta hun. mein kuchh logon ko isliye deta hun ke unke dilon mein ghabraahat aur be chainii hai aur doosrey logon par aitimad karta hun ke Allah ne unke dilon ko be niyaazii aur bhalai ata farmai hai. unhein mein se Amr bin taghlab bhi hain. Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us kalima ke muqaabla mein mujhey laal laal oont miltey to itni khushi na hoti .
7536,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab se riwayat kya ke Allah paak farmata hai ke jab banda mujh se aik baalisht qareeb hota hai to main aik hath us se qareeb hota hun aur jab banda mujh se aik hath qareeb hota hai to main us se 2 hath qareeb hota hun aur jab wo mere paas paidal chal kar aata hai to main daud kar aa jata hun.
7537,"aksar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) Allah Taala farmata hai ke) jab banda mujh se aik baalisht qareeb hota hai to main us se aik hath qareeb ho jata hun aur jab wo aik hath qareeb aata hai to main us se 2 hath qareeb hota hun aur Motamir ne kaha ke maine apne walid se suna, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne rab azz-w-jall se riwayat kartey they."
7538,"unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, Allah Taala se riwayat kartey hain ke parwardigar ne farmaya har gunah ka aik kaffara hai (jis se wo gunah maaf ho jata hai) aur roza khas mere liye hai aur main hi uski jazaa doonga aur roze-daar ke munh ki bo Allah ke nazdeek mushk ki khushbu se badh kar hai."
7539,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne parwardigar se riwayat kya parwardigar ne farmaya ke kisi bandey ke liye munasib nahi ke ye kahey ke main Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) se behtar hun aur aap ne Yunus (Alaihissalam) ko unke bap ki taraf nisbat di.
7540,maine fateh Makka ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apni aik ontni par Sawar they aur sura fateh padh rahe they ya sura fateh mein se kuchh aayatein padh rahe they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir aap ne usmein tarjeea' ki. Shoba ne kaha ye hadis bayan karke Muawiya ne is tarah awaz dohra kar qirat ki jaisey Abdullah-bin Mughaffal kya kartey they aur Muawiya ne kaha agar mujh ko iska khayal na hota ke log tumharey paas jama ho kar hujoom karengey to main isi tarah awaz dohra kar qirat karta jis tarah Abdullah-bin Mughaffal ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah awaz dohraney ko naql kya tha. Shoba ne kaha maine Muawiya se puchha ibne- Mughaffal kyon kar awaz dohraatey they? unhon-ne kaha aa teen-teen baar mad ke sath awaz dohraatey they.
7541,Hiraql ne apne tarjuman ko bulaya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khat mangwaya aur usey padha . shuru Allah ke naam se jo bahut bahut hi zyada raham karne wala bada meharban hai. Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se Hiraql ki taraf . phir ye aayat likhi thi (ya أهل الكتاب تعالوا إلى كلمة سواء بيننا وبينكم (ke ''aey kitab waalo! is baat par aa jao jo ham main tum mein yaksan maana jati hai'' aakhir aayat tak.
7542,"ahle-kitab Taurait ko Ibranii mein padhtey aur musalmanon ke liye uski tafseer arabii mein kartey they. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum na ahle-kitab ki tasdeeq karo aur na usko jhutlaao, balke kaho ke ham Allah aur uski tamam nazil ki hui kitaabon par eman laaey."
7543,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik Yahudi mard aur aurat laey gaey, jinhoney zina kya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahudiyon se puchha ke tum unke sath kya kartey ho? unhon-ne kaha ke ham unka munh kala karke unhein ruswa kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Taurait lao aur uski tilawat karo agar tum sachey ho chunanche wo ( Taurait ( laey aur aik shakhs se jis par wo mut'ma'in they kaha ke aey Aawar ! padho . chunanche us ne padha aur jab iske aik maqam par pahuncha to is par apna hath rakh diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apna hath uthao , jab us ne apna hath uthaya to usmein aayat rajm (sangsaar) bilkul waazeh taur par maujood thi, usne kaha : aey Muhammad ! un par rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm to waqei hai lekin ham usey aapas mein chhipaatey hain. chunanche donon rajm (sangsaar) kiye gaey, maine dekha ke mard aurat ko patthar se bachaney ke liye is par jhukaa padta tha."
7544,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala kisi cheez ko itni tawajjoh se nahi sunta jitni tawajjoh se achi awaz se padhney par Nabi ke Quran Majeed ko sunta hai."
7545,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baat ke silsile mein jab tohmat lagaaney walon ne un par tohmat lagai thi aur un rawiyon mein se har aik ne waqia ka eik-eik hissey bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bataya ke phir main rotey-rotey apne bistar par let gaee aur mujhey yaqin tha ke jab main us tohmat se barii hun to Allah Taala meri Bara't (Tauba) karega, lekin Allah ki qism ! iska mujhey guman bhi na tha ke mere barey mein Quran ki aayatein nazil hongi jinki qiyamat tak tilawat ki jaeygi aur mere khayal mein meri haisiyat is se bahut kam thi ke Allah mere barey mein paak kalam nazil farmaai jiski tilawat ho aur Allah Taala ne (sura Noor ki) ye aayat nazil ki) إن الذين جاءوا بالإفك‏ ( '' bila shubah wo log jinhoney tohmat lagai '' poori das aayaton tak."
7546,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap isha ki Namaz main ( والتين والزيتون‏ ( padh rahe they, maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada behtreen awaz se Quran padhtey huey kisi ko nahi suna."
7547,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka Mukarrama mein chhup kar tableegh kartey they, to Quran buland awaz se padhtey, mushrekeen jab suntey to Quran ko bura bhala kehtey aur uske laney waley ko bura bhala kehtey. is par Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya ke '' apni Namaz mein na awaz buland karo aur na bahut past .''"
7548,unhon-ne unse kaha mera khayal hai ke tum bakriyon ko aur jangal ko pasand kartey ho. to jab tum apni bakriyon mein ya jangal mein ho aur Namaz ke liye azan do to buland awaz ke sath do kyonke muazzan ki awaz jahan tak bhi pahunchegii aur usey jin w insan aur dusri jo cheezein bhi sunengii wo qiyamat ke din uski gawahi dengii. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine is hadis ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai.
7549,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt bhi Quran padhtey they jab aap ka sar Mubarak meri god mein hota aur main haalat haiz mein hoti .
7550,"maine Hisham-bin-Hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein sura furqan padhtey suna. maine dekha ke wo Quran Majeed bahut se aisey tariqon se padh rahe they jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein nahi padhaaey they. qareeb tha ke Namaz hi mein un par main halla kar dun lekin maine sabr se kaam liya aur jab unhon-ne salam phera to maine unki gardan main apni chadar ka phandaa laga diya aur unse kaha tumhen ye sura is tarah kis ne padhai jisey maine abhi tum se suna. unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey is tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne padhai hai. maine kaha tum jhootey ho, mujhey khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mukhtalif qirat sikhai hai jo tum padh rahe they. chunanche main unhein kheenchtaa hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley gaya aur arz kya ke maine is shakhs ko sura furqan is tarah padhtey suna jo aap ne mujhey nahi sikhaaii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein chhod do. Hisham ! tum padh kar sunao. unhon-ne wahi qirat padhi jo main unse sun chuka tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke isi tarah ye sura nazil hui hai. aey umr ! ab tum padho ! maine us qirat ke mutabiq padha jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sikhai thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is tarah bhi nazil hui hai. ye Quran Arab ki saat (7) boliyon par utara gaya hai. to tumhen jis qirat mein sahoolat ho padho."
7551,maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! phir amal karne waley kis liye amal kartey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har shakhs ke liye us amal mein aasani paida kar di gaee hai jiske liye wo paida kya gaya hai.
7552,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik janaaza mein they phir aap ne aik lakdi li aur us se zameen kuredney lagey. phir farmaya tum mein koi aisa nahi jiska thikana jahannam mein ya jannat mein likha na ja chuka ho. sahaba ne kaha : phir ham isi par bharosa na kar lein ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har shakhs ke liye us amal mein aasani paida kar di gaee jiske liye wo paida kya gaya hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhi ( فأما من أعطى واتقى‏ (ke ''jis shakhs ne bakhshish ki aur taqwa ikhtiyar kya '' aakhir aayat tak.
7553,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala jab khilqat ka paida karna thehra chuka (ya jab khilqat paida kar chukaa) to usne arsh ke uper apne paas aik kitab likh kar rakhi usmein yun hai meri rehmat mere ghussey par ghalib hai ya mere ghussey se aagey badh chuki hai.''
7554,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne makhlooq ko paida karne se pahley aik tahreer likhi ke meri rehmat mere ghazab se badh kar hai, chunanche ye uske paas arsh ke uper likha hua hai."
7555,"is qabila jurm aur ash-ariyon mein mohabbat aur bhai chaara ka mamla tha. aik martaba ham abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they ke unke paas khana laya gaya jis mein murghi ka gosht bhi tha. unke yahan aik bani taimillaah ka bhi shakhs tha. ghaaliban wo Arab ke ghulam logon mein se tha. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apne paas bulaya to usne kaha ke maine murghi ko gandagi khaatey dekha hai aur usi waqt se qism kha li ke iska gosht nahi khaaunga. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, suno! main tum se iske mutaalliq aik hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bayan karta hun. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ash-ariyon ke kuchh afraad ko lekar hazir hua aur ham ne aap se sawari maangii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qasam! main tumharey liye sawari ka intizam nahi kar sakta, na mere paas koi aisi cheez hai jisey main tumhen sawari ke liye dun. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas maale-ghanimat mein se kuchh oont aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey mutaalliq puchha ke Ash-ari log kahan hain? chunanche aap ne hamein panch umda oont dene ka hukm diya. ham unhein lekar chaley to ham ne apne amal ke mutaalliq sochaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism khaaii thi ke hamein sawari ke liye koi janwar nahi dengey aur na aap ke paas koi aisa janwar hai jo hamein sawari ke liye dein. ham ne sochaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni qism bhool gaey hain, Allah ki qasam! ham kabhi falaah nahi pa saktey. ham wapas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunchey aur aap se soorate-haal ke mutaalliq poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen ye sawari nahi de raha hun balke Allah de raha hai. Allah ki qasam! main agar koi qism kha leta hun aur phir iske khilaf mein dekhta hun to main wahi karta hun jis mein bhalai hoti hai aur qism ka kaffara de deta hun."
7556,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : to aap ne farmaya ke qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur unhon-ne kaha ke hamarey aur aap ke darmyan qabila muzr ke mushrekeen rukawat hain aur ham aap ke paas sirf hurmat waley mahinon mein hi aa saktey hain. isliye aap kuchh aisey jaame' ehkaam hamein bata dijiye ke agar ham un par amal karein to jannat mein jayen aur unki taraf un logon ko dawat dein jo hamarey peechhey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char kaamon ka hukm deta hun aur char kaamon se roktaa hun. main tumhen eman billah ka hukm deta hun. tumhen malum hai ke eman billah kya hai? iski gawahi dena hai ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur Namaz qaaim karna aur zakat dene aur ghaneemat mein se panchwan hissey dene ka hukm deta hun aur tumhen char kaamon se roktaa hon, ye ke kadu ki tonbii aur lakdi ke kuredey huey bartan aur roghanii bartanon aur sabz laakhii bartanon mein mat piyaa karo."
7557,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''un tasweeron ko banaaney walon par qiyamat mein azab hoga aur unse kaha jaeyga ke tum ne jo banaya hai usey zinda bhi karke dikhaao.''
7558,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''un tasweeron ko banaaney walon par qiyamat mein azab hoga aur unse kaha jaeyga ke tum ne jo banaya hai usey zinda bhi karo.''
7559,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah farmata hai ke us shakhs se badh kar had se tajaawuz karne wala aur kon hai jo meri makhlooq ki tarah makhlooq banata hai, zara wo chaney ka daana paida karke to dekhein ya gehun ka aik daana ya jau ka aik daana paida karke to dekhein."
7560,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us momin ki misal jo Quran padhta hai turanj ki si hai ke iska maza bhi achchha aur uski khushbu bhi umda hai aur wo momin jo nahi padhta khajoor ki tarah hai ke uska maza to achchha hai lekin usmein khushbu nahi aur us fasiq ki misal jo Quran padhta hai murda ki tarah hai ke uski khushbu to achi hai lekin iska maza kadwaa hai aur jo fasiq Quran nahi padhta uski misal indraayan ki si hai ke uska maza bhi kadwaa hai aur koi khushbu bhi nahi.''
7561,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke kuchh logon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaahinon ke mutaalliq sawal kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unki kisi baat ka eitibaar nahi. aik sahib ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ye log kuchh aisi baatein bayan kartey hain jo sahi Sabit hoti hain. bayan kya ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye sahi baat wo hai jisey shaitan farishton se sun kar yad rakh leta hai aur phir usey murghi ke kat kat karne ki tarah ( kaahinon (ke kanon mein daal deta hai aur ye usmein so se zyada jhoot milaate hain.
7562,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kuchh log mashriq ki taraf se niklengey aur Quran padhengey jo unke halaq se nichey nahi utreyga, ye log Deen se is tarah door phenk diye jaeinge jaisey teer phenk diya jata hai. phir ye log kabhi Deen mein nahi wapas aa saktey, yahan tak ke teer apni jagah ( khud ( wapas aa jaey, puchha gaya ke unki pehchan kya hogii? to farmaya ke unki alamat sar mundwana hogi.''"
7563,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''2 kalimey aisey hain jo Allah tabarak w taala ko bahut hi pasand hain jo zaban par halkey hain aur qiyamat ke din aamaal ke taraazu mein bojhal aur baa-wazn hongey, wo kalimaat mubaraka ye hain ( sub'haanallaahi-w-bi-hamdihi, Mina sub'haanallaahil-azeem).''"
